%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bad%20weather%2C%20natural%20disasters%2C%20and%20disease%20are%20hobbling%20crops%20right%20now.%20Here's%20how%20the%20food%20commodity%20markets%20are%20responding.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221510%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rice%20Paddy%20Japan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d4ef9b4dd2b50019c2c441%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221131%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EiStock%2F%20Sean%20Pavone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENatural%20catastrophes%20and%20bad%20weather%20have%20wreaked%20havoc%20on%20food%20crops%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOrange%20juice%20futures%2C%20cacao%20beans%2C%20and%20rice%20have%20hit%20all-time%20highs%20of%20late%20%E2%80%93%20while%20Chinese%20pork%20has%20slumped.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHere's%20a%20round-up%20of%20the%20main%20movements%20in%20food%20commodity%20prices%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENatural%20disasters%2C%20adverse%20weather%2C%20and%20invasive%20diseases%20have%20all%20helped%20wreak%20havoc%20on%20the%20market%20for%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20important%20foodstuffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20succession%20of%20hurricanes%20and%20deadly%20bacteria%20have%20ravaged%20American%20oranges%2C%20while%20heavy%20rainfall%20has%20rotted%20cacao%20beans%20in%20West%20Africa.%20As%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20Asian%20rice%20hit%20its%20highest%20price%20in%20almost%2015%20years%3B%20while%20in%20China%2C%20pork%20prices%20have%20slumped%20so%20far%20that%20they%20have%20dragged%20inflation%20into%20negative%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20roundup%20of%20what's%20been%20happening%20in%20the%20world%20of%20soft%20commodities%20lately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrange%20juice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOrange%20juice%20futures%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%20on%20July%2028%2C%20as%20citrus%20crops%20all%20across%20the%20US%20have%20been%20hammered%20by%20a%20series%20of%20hurricanes%20and%20the%20spread%20of%20'citrus%20greening'%2C%20an%20incurable%20disease%20spread%20by%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ICE%20US%20frozen%20orange%20futures%20index%C2%A0touched%20a%20record%20317.5%20(USc%20per%20lb)%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20a%20metric%20that%20reflects%20orange%20juice%20production%20in%20the%20US%20as%20the%20lowest%20in%20%26quot%3Bover%20100%20years%26quot%3B%2C%20Matthew%20Joyner%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20Florida%20Citrus%20Mutual%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fab06eadb-1de6-45e8-89c7-50531614d9a8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20oranges%20produced%20in%20the%20US%20come%20from%20Florida%2C%20which%20has%20been%20hobbled%20by%20hurricanes%20and%20a%20cold%20snap%2C%20massively%20hampering%20supply.%20Not%20only%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%2C%20but%20the%20resurgence%20of%20the%20pathogen%2C%C2%A0%20has%20ravaged%20crops%20in%20both%20America%20and%20Brazil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20headwinds%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20supply%20shortage%20in%20oranges%2C%20which%20has%20driven%20up%20prices%20that%20will%20eventually%20filter%20through%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChinese%20pork%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fchina-pork-prices-have-fallen-dragging-country-into-deflation-2023-8%5C%22%3EChinese%20pork%20prices%20have%20fallen%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20over%20a%20quarter%20since%20the%20previous%20July%20as%20an%20oversupply%20of%20meat%20has%20weighed%20heavily%20on%20consumer%20food%20prices%2C%20pushing%20the%20Asian%20state%20into%20a%20period%20of%20deflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPork%20plays%20an%20important%20part%20in%20the%20makeup%20of%20China's%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20basket%2C%20accounting%20for%20around%203%25%20of%20it%2C%20per%20the%20Economist%20Intelligence%20Unit.%20%26quot%3BA%20rough%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20therefore%20that%20a%2010%25%20increase%20in%20the%20pork%20price%20will%20push%20up%20the%20CPI%20by%200.3%25%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountry.eiu.com%2Farticle.aspx%3Farticleid%3D636856447%26Country%3DChina%26topic%3DEconomy%26oid%3D1092669893%26flid%3D357283419%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20EIU%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20research%20note%2C%20underscoring%20the%20animal's%20importance%20to%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Statistics%20showed%20that%20pork%20prices%20have%20fallen%2026%25%20in%20July%20year-on-year%2C%20a%20significant%20fall%20for%20the%20world's%20largest%20producer%20and%20consumer%20of%20the%20meat.%20The%20decline%20in%20prices%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20oversupply%20in%20the%20market%2C%20caused%20by%20a%20backlog%20after%20a%20bad%20outbreak%20of%20African%20swine%20fever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECocoa%20beans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOrange%20juice%20is%20not%20the%20only%20sweet%20to%20see%20its%20value%20jump%20recently%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Monday%2C%20cocoa%20bean%20futures%20surged%20to%20their%20highest%20levels%20since%202011%2C%20according%20to%20data%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barchart.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2F19234096%2Fcocoa-prices-under-pressure-from-improved-weather-in-west-africa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarchart%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beans%2C%20used%20primarily%20in%20chocolate%2C%20are%20rallying%20amid%20a%20supply%20crunch%20caused%20by%20heavy%20rainfall%20and%20the%20spread%20of%20a%20black%20pod%20disease%20in%20West%20Africa%2C%20which%20has%20rotted%20cocoa%20pods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spread%20of%20the%20blight%20caused%20by%20the%20extreme%20wet%20weather%20could%20result%20in%20lower%20crop%20quality%20and%20production%2C%20pushing%20the%20global%20cocoa%20market%20into%20a%20third%20year%20of%20deficit%20for%20the%202023%2F24%20season%2C%20according%20to%20Barchart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAsian%20rice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERice%20has%20not%20been%20this%20expensive%20in%20almost%2015%20years%2C%20as%20exceptionally%20dry%20weather%20in%20Thailand%20and%20India%20and%20the%20banning%20of%20its%20own%20exports%20foster%20a%20global%20shortage%20in%20the%20crop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20Thai%20white%20rice%205%25%20broken%20has%20hit%20%24648%20a%20ton%20%E2%80%93%20the%20highest%20since%20October%202008%20%E2%80%93%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-08-09%2Frice-in-asia-soars-to-highest-level-since-2008-on-supply-risks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Thai%20Rice%20Exporters%20Association%20released%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20onset%20of%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%2C%20where%20water%20temperature%20in%20the%20Pacific%20rises%2C%20Thai%20farmers%20are%20being%20encouraged%20to%20switch%20to%20growing%20crops%20that%20require%20less%20water.%20While%20India%2C%20another%20key%20producer%2C%20last%20month%20extended%20its%20export%20ban%20to%20protect%20domestic%20supply%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20has%20increased%20fears%20of%20a%20supply%20shortage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERice%20is%20integral%20to%20the%20diets%20of%20billions%20of%20people%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20and%20a%20shortage%20may%20potentially%20spell%20catastrophe%20for%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-commodity-markets-fluctuate-bad-weather-and-disasters-hit-crops-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691931479000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d4ef9b4dd2b50019c2c441%3Fformat%3Dj