ment.%20And%20they%20are%20not%20obligated%20to%20be%20factually%20right.%20Misrepresentation%20in%20parliament%20is%20a%20big%20crime.%20But%20why%20is%20this%20not%20our%20concern%3F%20Why%20are%20falsehood%2C%20half-truths%20by%20the%20government%20being%20accepted%20as%20legitimate%20given%20that%20they%20help%20it%20in%20navigating%20through%20the%20debate%3F%20Is%20this%20not%20considered%20as%20cheating%20the%20people%20of%20India%3F%20Leave%20alone%20asking%20these%20questions%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20being%20praised%20for%20having%20come%20of%20age%20and%20is%20lauded%20as%20an%20ace%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rhetoric%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20his%20specialty.%20That%20he%20is%20crass%2C%20uncouth%2C%20vicious%20is%20considered%20necessary%20for%20his%20popularity.%20His%20aggressive%20and%20violent%20language%20has%20come%20to%20be%20considered%20appropriate%20for%20the%20person%20of%20the%20highest%20position%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20in%20the%20media%20are%20saying%20in%20a%20hushed%20voice%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20should%20have%20said%20something%20more%20on%20Manipur.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20say%20that%20how%20can%20it%20be%20accepted%20that%20the%20most%20important%20subject%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Manipur%2C%20was%20considered%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20be%20worth%20only%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%5C%22%3Eless%20than%20ten%20minutes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20two-hour%20speech.%20That%20too%20was%20nothing%20but%20empty%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20is%20with%20Manipur%20or%20this%20House%20is%20with%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%20is%20no%20consolation%20to%20the%20violence-torn%20state.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20problem%20of%20Manipur.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20minority%20Kuki%20population%20of%20Manipur%20is%20saying%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20not%20with%20them.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20Manipur%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20parts%20and%20both%20have%20become%20enemies%20of%20each%20other.%20%E2%80%98That%20the%20sun%20of%20peace%20will%20rise%20on%20Manipur%E2%80%99%20is%20no%20assurance%20for%20the%20victims%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20Such%20empty%20rhetoric%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%20when%20the%20opposition%20wants%20to%20know%20what%20steps%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20But%20the%20media%20has%20declared%20victory%20for%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Manipur%20appeared%20not%20to%20be%20an%20issue%20of%20importance%20for%20the%20prime%20minister.%20It%20was%20very%20clear%20from%20the%20space%20that%20he%20gave%20to%20Manipur%20in%20his%20two-hour%20long%20speech.%20It%20was%20all%20about%20himself.%20When%20he%20was%20giving%20the%20speech%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Emassive%20violence%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20Haryana%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20near%20Delhi%2C%20due%20to%20the%20negligence%20or%20connivance%20of%20his%20own%20party%E2%80%99s%20government.%20And%20after%20that%2C%20the%20government%20unleashed%20massive%20violence%20on%20the%20Muslims%2C%20arresting%20them%20indiscriminately%20and%20bulldozing%20their%20houses%20and%20shops.%20But%20in%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20this%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fspecial-days-before-mha-was-to-finalise-kuki-accord-not-supported-by-cm-violence-broke-out-in-manipur%5C%22%3ESpecial%3A%20Manipur%20Violence%20Broke%20Out%20Days%20Before%20Mha%20Was%20to%20Finalise%20Kuki%20Accord%20That%20CM%20Did%20Not%20Support%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForget%20a%20word%20of%20regret%20or%20condemnation.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20word%20of%20consolation%20for%20those%20killed.%20Will%20the%20opposition%20have%20to%20bring%20a%20new%20no-confidence%20motion%20for%20Haryana%20as%20well%20so%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20or%20the%20Union%20government%20open%20their%20mouths%3F%20After%20the%20violence%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnuh-demolitions-haryana-govt-tells-hc-that-due-process-was-followed-denies-ethnic-cleansing%5C%22%3Emade%20a%20strong%20comment%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20bulldozing%20of%20the%20Muslim%20houses%20and%20termed%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Cethnic%20cleansing%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20behaving%20as%20if%20nothing%20has%20happened.%20Thousands%20of%20people%20have%20become%20homeless%20near%20Delhi%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20laughing%20and%20joking%20with%20his%20courtier%20MPs%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20an%20insult%20to%20Manipur.%20There%20was%20no%20regret%2C%20no%20trace%20of%20sympathy%20for%20the%20plight%20of%20Manipur%20in%20the%20speeches%20of%20Modi%20and%20Shah.%20No%20matter%20how%20much%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20clap%20and%20dance%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%20must%20be%20worried%20about%20the%20cruel%20self-obsession%20of%20their%20rulers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20those%20who%20still%20have%20humanity%20left%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20debate%20and%20the%20response%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20minister%20left%20feelings%20of%20sadness%2C%20despair%2C%20anger%20and%20shame.%20Do%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%2C%20do%20we%20deserve%20this%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20great%20pity%20that%20the%20members%20of%20the%20government%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20the%20BJ