p%20to%20660%20feet%20away%2C%20per%20Howstuffworks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HRW%20said%20it%20had%20found%20instances%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcat-uxo.com%2Fexplosive-hazards%2Flandmines%2Fozm-72-landmine%5C%22%3EOZM-72%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bbounding%20fragmentation%26quot%3B%20mines%20being%20used%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20organization%20described%20the%20OZM-72%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmulti-purpose%20bounding%20munition.%26quot%3B%20It%20adds%20that%20when%20the%20mine%20is%20%26quot%3Bused%20in%20victim-activated%20mode%20with%20a%20mechanical%20pull%2C%20tension%20release%2C%20or%20seismic%20fuze%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20are%20prohibited%20by%20the%20Mine%20Ban%20Treaty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAnti-tank%20mines%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224444%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anti-tank%20mines%20at%20a%20Russian%20position%20taken%20under%20control%20by%20the%20Ukrainian%20army%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Velyka%20Novosilka%2C%2013%20July%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d2ae0d11d6ad0019ed7a27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnti-tank%20mines%20at%20a%20Russian%20position%20taken%20under%20control%20by%20the%20Ukrainian%20army%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Velyka%20Novosilka%2C%2013%20July%202023.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Diego%20Herrera%20Carcedo%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Anti-tank%20blast%20mines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnti-tank%20mines%20are%20much%20larger%20versions%20of%20anti-personnel%20blast%20mines%2C%20designed%20to%20cause%20maximum%20damage%20to%20tanks%20by%20destroying%20their%20tracks%20and%20piercing%20their%20armor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20also%20pressure%20activated%2C%20but%20they%20usually%20take%20a%20much%20greater%20force%20to%20be%20triggered%20%E2%80%94%20about%20348.33%20pounds%20to%20745.16%20pounds%2C%20per%20Howstuffworks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20has%20seen%20a%20variety%20of%20anti-tank%20mines%20used%2C%20including%20the%20PTM-1%20and%20the%20TM-62M.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HRW%20says%20that%20the%20PTM-1%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20plastic-bodied%2C%20rectangular%20mine%26quot%3B%20that%20is%20dropped%20by%20a%20helicopter%20or%20scattered%20by%20rocket%20artillery.%20It%20notes%20that%20both%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20have%20supplies%20of%20the%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TM-62M%2C%20it%20adds%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20large%2C%20metal-cased%20circular%20mine%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20either%20be%20mechanically%20placed%20or%20laid%20by%20hand.%20It%20says%20both%20sides%20also%20have%20stockpiles%20of%20this%20type%20of%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMine%20warfare%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20forces%20have%20relied%20heavily%20on%20dense%20minefields%20during%20the%20invasion%2C%20especially%20in%20response%20to%20Ukraine's%20counteroffensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20depth%20of%20the%20minefields%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-russia-defenses-ukraine-effective-mines-drones-experts-2023-8%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Emulti-layered%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20Russians%20lay%20several%20mines%20on%20top%20of%20each%20other%20to%20destroy%20mine-clearing%20equipment%2C%20has%20even%20forced%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminefields-force-ukraine-to-change-counteroffensive-strategy-russia-2023-7%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20to%20abandon%20their%20long-awaited%20Western-made%20tanks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20advance%20on%20foot%2C%20as%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20had%20to%20change%20its%20counteroffensive%20strategy%20this%20summer%20after%20early%20assaults%20by%20tanks%20and%20fighting%20vehicles%20became%20stuck%20in%20fields%20bobby%20trapped%20with%20mines.%20They%20were%20easily%20picked%20off%20by%20Russian%20artillery%20and%20attack%20drones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20military%20personnel%20receive%20armored%20maneuver%20training%20on%20German-made%20Leopard%202%20battle%20tanks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d3aade11d6ad0019ee01aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20military%20personnel%20receive%20armored%20maneuver%20training%20on%20German-made%20Leopard%202%20battle%20tanks%3Cp%3EOSCAR%20DEL%20POZO%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20limitations%20of%20vehicles%20like%20the%20US-made%20Bradley%20armored%20fighting%20vehicle%20became%20clear%2C%20Ukraine's%20commander-in-chief%20General%20Valery%20Zaluzhny%20demanded%20modern%20fighter%20jets%20like%20the%20US-made%20F-16%20to%20improve%20its%20ground%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20no%20longer%20do%20anything%20with%20just%20a%20tank%20with%20some%20armor%20because%20the%20minefield%20is%20too%20deep%2C%20and%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20it%20will%20stop%2C%20and%20then%20it%20will%20be%20destroyed%20by%20concentrated%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20Zaluzhny%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F07%2F15%2Fukraine-war-russia-mines-counteroffensive%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-types-landmines-how-they-work-bounding-anti-tank-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691928140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d2ae377d2e90001946ba7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-types-landmines-how-they-work-bounding-anti-tank