20she%20added%2C%20it%20could%20improve%20her%20income.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBase%20pay%20for%20DoorDash%20orders%20is%20as%20low%20as%20%242%2C%20making%20tips%20a%20key%20source%20of%20income%20for%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDoorDash's%20tip%20nudges%20come%20as%20some%20delivery%20workers%20have%20aggressively%20attempted%20to%20increase%20tips.%20Some%20delivery%20workers%20have%20tried%20to%20increase%20their%20gratuity%20by%20asking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-drivers-want-extra-tips-before-delivery-customers-complain-2023-5%5C%22%3EDoorDash%20customers%20for%20higher%20tips%3C%2Fa%3E%20mid-delivery.%20In%20other%20cases%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrivers-shame-customers-tips-doordash-tipping-culture-2023-7%5C%22%3EDashers%20have%20shamed%20customers%20over%20low%20tips.%3C%2Fa%3E%20DoorDash%20prohibits%20these%20sorts%20of%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoorDash's%20nudges%20will%20appear%20for%20customers%20who%20have%20not%20already%20added%20a%20tip%20to%20their%20order.%20%26quot%3BCustomers%20get%20a%20maximum%20of%20one%20nudge%20per%20order%20that%20does%20not%20include%20a%20tip%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20unique%20to%20DoorDash%20and%20is%20common%20practice%20across%20gig%20platforms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20and%20Instacart%20are%20a%20bit%20more%20intrusive%20with%20their%20tip%20nudging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221872%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoorDash%20post-checkout%20tipping%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649b3c006eb0a800194d6339%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221786%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDoorDash%20introduced%20post-checkout%20tipping.%3Cp%3EDoorDash%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20rolled%20out%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D104dd84f65b