re%20on%20delivery%20and%20have%20earned%20more%20per%20active%20hour%20every%20year%20for%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20DoorDash%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMany%20gig%20delivery%20workers%20make%20below%20minimum%20wage%20and%20say%20their%20earnings%20have%20fallen%20since%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%202020%20study%20found%20many%20gig%20delivery%20workers%20are%20struggling%20to%20make%20minimum%20wage.%20The%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshift.hks.harvard.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2Fgig_brief.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20survey%20of%20gig%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Economic%20Policy%20Institute%20found%20that%20about%2014%25%20of%20gig%20workers%20made%20less%20than%20the%20federal%20minimum%20wage%2C%20and%2029%25%20earned%20less%20than%20their%20state's%20minimum%20wage.%20The%20survey%20was%20conducted%20in%202020%2C%20a%20banner%20year%20for%20gig%20workers%20due%20to%20demand%20for%20delivery%20early%20in%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwTvRNwslYxA%26list%3DPLF4ij7xFI0e9RIXcIFplbEVxqvwHC1VlL%26index%3D9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enumber%20of%20people%20working%20gig%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20grew%20sharply%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20But%20since%20then%2C%20demand%20for%20delivery%20has%20declined%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffoodondemand.com%2F06212023%2Fu-s-online-grocery-sales-dip-to-6-9-billion%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGrocery%2520delivery%2520declined%252011.7%2520percent%2Corders%2520than%2520they%2520used%2520to.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparticularly%20in%20grocery.%3C%2Fa%3E%20That%20leaves%20fewer%20orders%20for%20more%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225973%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20driver%20for%20food%20delivery%20service%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20rides%20a%20bicycle%20with%20a%20transport%20box%20on%20his%20back%20on%20a%20street%20in%20the%20Friedrichshain%20district%20of%20Berlin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d6aaab1f51cc0019683b87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Uber%20Eats%20app%20also%20'nudges'%20customers%20to%20tip.%3Cp%3ECarsten%20Koall%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESergio%20Avedian%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherideshareguy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20The%20Rideshare%20Guy%3C%2Fa%3E%20blog%20who%20delivers%20about%2020%20hours%20a%20week%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20said%20his%20base%20pay%20ranges%20on%20DoorDash%20or%20Uber%20Eats%20from%20%241.50%20to%20%243%20per%20order%20%E2%80%94%2050%25%20less%20than%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic%20when%20earnings%20surged%20due%20to%20demand.%20Other%20drivers%20speaking%20to%20Insider%20quoted%20similar%20declining%20base%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20base%20pay%20is%20so%20low%2C%20we%20have%20to%20look%20for%20high-tip%2C%20low-mileage%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20literally%20working%20for%20tips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20delivery%20driver%20with%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Got%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20nluna%40insider.com%20or%20text%20at%20714-269-8873.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-tip-nudges-latest-example-importantance-tipping-gig-workers-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691927401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d6ab071f51cc0019683bb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-tip-nudges-latest-example-importantance-tipping-gig-workers-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22DoorDash%20is%20the%20latest%20delivery%20service%20to%20nudge%20customers%20who%20don't%20tip.%20It%20shows%20how%20intrusive%20tip%20requests%20are%2C%20and%20how%20important%20tips%20are%20to%20gig%20workers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nluna%40insider.com%20(Nancy%20Luna%2CAlex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-tip-nudges-latest-example-importantance-tipping-gig-workers-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Was%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20Election%20Manipulated%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F11193837%2Ftezpur-ec.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4512936%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Ashoka%20University%20scholar%20Sabyasachi%20Das%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Democratic%20Backsliding%20in%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Largest%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20seems%20to%20have%20stirred%20the%20hornet%E2%80%99s%20nest%20in%20certain%20political%20circles.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDas%20published%20this%20paper%20in%20the%20background%20of%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20being%20called%20into%20question%2C%20with%20allegations%20of%20bias%20in%20scheduling%20of%20elections%20and%20arbitrary%20deletions%20of%20the%20names%20of%20registered%20Muslim%20voters.%20Both%20of%20these%20will%20have%20favoured%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20reports%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-autocratiser-v-dem-report-2023%5C%22%3EV-Dem%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-remained-partly-free-in-2022-says-us-government-funded-think-tank%5C%22%3E%20Freedom%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%20questioning%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20credentials.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20Das%E2%80%99s%20findings%20are%20deeply%20disturbing%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20The%202019%20general%20election%20that%20reelected%20the%20incumbent%20party%20shows%20significant%20irregularities%20in%20election%20data.%20The%20density%20of%20the%20incumbent%20party%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20win%20margin%20variable%20exhibits%20a%20discontinuous%20jump%20at%20the%20threshold%20value%20of%20zero.%20It%20implies%20that%20in%20constituencies%20that%20were%20closely%20contested%20between%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20incumbent%20party%20and%20a%20rival%2C%20the%20incumbent%20party%20won%20disproportionately%20more%20of%20them%20than%20lost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cspan%3E2.%20There%20were%20no%20similar%20discontinuities%20in%20the%20previous%20general%20elections%20for%20either%20BJP%20or%20Congress%2C%20the%20other%20major%20national%20party%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20state%20assembly%20elections%20held%20simultaneously%20with%20the%202019%20general%20election%20and%20those%20held%20subsequently.%20Moreover%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20disproportionate%20win%20of%20closely%20contested%20constituencies%20is%20primarily%20concentrated%20in%20states%20ruled%20by%20the%20party%20at%20the%20time%20of%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E3.%20Electoral%20manipulation%20can%20take%20place%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20voter%20registration%20(registration%20manipulation)%20or%20at%20the%20time%20of%20voting%20or%20counting%20(turnout%20manipulation).%20However%2C%20the%20overall%20extent%20of%20manipulation%20in%20the%202019%20general%20election%20was%20not%20in%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20paper%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20focuses%20on%20closely%20contested%20constituencies%20to%20detect%20the%20presence%20of%20potential%20manipulation.%20The%20paper%20has%20shed%20light%20on%20around%2011%20parliament%20constituencies%20where%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20win%20margin%20was%20less%20than%205%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scholar%20opines%20that%20though%20the%20size%20of%20the%20alleged%20manipulation%20is%20small%2C%20the%20results%20signify%20a%20worrying%20development%20for%20the%20future%20of%20democracy%20in%20India%20and%20consequently%2C%20in%20the%20world%20at%20large.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20if%20unchecked%20and%20given%20technological%20advancement%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20these%20alleged%20manipulations%20could%20be%20substantially%20scaled%20up%20in%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdemocracy-voting-evm-vvpat-modi-election%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20Will%20of%20the%20People%20to%20the%20Whim%20of%20the%20Machines%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20inexplicably%2C%20Das%20did%20not%20consider%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20manipulation%20of%20Electronic%20Voter%20Machines%20or%20EVMs%20themselves%20as%20a%20mechanism%2C%20%E2%80%9Cas%20Purkayastha%20and%20Sinha%20(2019)%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20given%20its%20technology%2C%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20manipulate%20them%20at%20scale.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20ample%20material%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20questioning%20the%20sanctity%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20process%20mainly%20due%20to%20severe%20flaws%20in%20EVM%20voting%20and%20voter-verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%20counting.%20These%20do%20not%20comply%20with%20essential%20electoral%20and%20democracy%20requirements%20of%20end-to-end%20verifiability%20and%20principles%20which%20stipulate%20that%20each%20voter%20have%20the%20knowledge%20and%20capacity%20to%20verify%20that%20their%20vote%20is%20cast%20as%20intended%2C%20recorded%20as%20cast%20and%20counted%20as%20recorded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20arranged%20for%20all%20EVMs%20to%20be%20accompanied%20with%20VVPAT%20for%20the%202019%20parliament%20elections.%20Experts%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%3C%2Fem%3E-like%20way%20the%20VVPAT-device%20has%20been%20inserted%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20electronic%20voting%20process%20has%20endangered%20security%20and%20that%20the%20process%20safeguards%20that%20were%20earlier%20designed%20to%20protect%20EVMs%20have%20lost%20their%20value.%20The%20fact%20is%20that%20though%20the%20device%20is%20called%20%E2%80%9Cvoter-verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%E2%80%9D%20it%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20the%20level%20of%20a%20fancy%20bioscope%20which%20shows%20a%20tiny%20paper%20slip%20for%20seven%20seconds%20which%20then%20vanishes%20and%20is%2C%20significantly%2C%20not%20counted.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20semblance%20of%20verifiability%20by%20the%20voter%2C%20only%20a%20brief%20sighting.%20It%20is%20a%20grand%20deception%20being%20played%20on%20the%20Indian%20voter%20who%20is%20exercising%20her%20fundamental%20right%20to%20elect%20her%20representative%20to%20govern%20the%20country%20on%20her%20behalf.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20matter%2C%20so%20crucial%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%2C%20went%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202018.%20On%20April%208%2C%202019%2C%20the%20court%20disposed%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20saying%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%5BO%5Dur%20considered%20view%20is%20that%20having%20regard%20to%20the%20totality%20of%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20case%20and%20need%20to%20generate%20the%20greatest%20degree%20of%20satisfaction%20in%20all%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20full%20accuracy%20of%20the%20election%20results%2C%20the%20number%20of%20EVMs%20that%20would%20now%20be%20subjected%20to%20verification%20so%20far%20as%20VVPAT%20paper%20trail%20is%20concerned%20would%20be%205%20per%20Assembly%20Constituency%20or%20Assembly%20Segments%20in%20a%20Parliamentary%20Constituency%20instead%20of%20what%20is%20provided%20by%20Guideline%20No.%2016.6%2C%20namely%2C%20one%20machine%20per%20Assembly%20Constituency%20or%20Assembly%20Segment%20in%20a%20Parliamentary%20Constituency%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20increased%20the%20sample%20size%20from%20microscopic%200.5%25%20to%20a%20minuscule%202%25%20against%20the%20demand%20for%2030%25%20to%2050%25.%20The%20court%20also%20summarily%20dismissed%20the%20review%20petition%20on%20May%207%2C%202019.%20The%20request%20to%20the%20ECI%20to%20count%20at%20least%20manually%20the%20measly%202%25%20VVPAT%20slips%20upfront%20and%20do%20the%20verification%20before%20the%20main%20electronic%20count%20was%20rudely%20rejected.%20In%20the%20event%2C%20in%20the%202019%20election%2C%20not%20even%20one%20VVPAT%20slip%20was%20counted%20and%20matched%20before%20the%20entire%20electronic%20count%20was%20done%20and%20results%20were%20made%20public.%20This%20gave%20rise%20to%20the%20distinct%20possibility%20of%20voting%20and%20counting%20manipulation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeeply%20perturbed%20by%20the%20massive%20discrepancies%20between%20the%20votes%20polled%20and%20votes%20counted%2C%20ADR%20and%20Common%20Cause%20filed%20a%20writ%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202019%20itself.%20Here%20is%20a%20relevant%20extract%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20as%20per%20the%20research%20conducted%20by%20a%20team%20of%20experts%20with%20the%20petitioner%20organization%20there%20have%20been%20serious%20discrepancies%20between%20the%20number%20of%20voters%20in%20different%20constituencies%20(i.e.%2C%20the%20voter%20turnout%20data%20collated%20and%20provided%20by%20the%20ECI)%20and%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20counted.%20That%20the%20study%20of%20the%20discrepancy%20patterns%20in%20all%20the%20constituencies%20based%20on%20the%20data%20made%20available%20on%20the%20main%20website%20of%20the%20ECI%20and%20so%20also%20the%20%E2%80%98My%20Voters%20turnout%20App%E2%80%99%20has%20given%20the%20following%20conclusions%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20Master%20summary%20of%20542%20constituencies%20shows%20discrepancies%20in%20347%20seats%20and%20the%20discrepancies%20range%20from%201%20vote%20(lowest)%20to%201%2C01%2C323%20votes%20%40%2010.49%25%20of%20the%20total%20votes%20(highest).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%206%20seats%20where%20the%20discrepancy%20in%20votes%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20winning%20margin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20total%20volume%20of%20discrepancies%20is%207%2C39%2C104%20votes%20put%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Before%20Celebrating%20'Remote%20Voting'%2C%20EC%20Should%20Address%20Longstanding%20Questions%20on%20the%20EVM%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbefore-celebrating-remote-voting-ec-should-address-longstanding-questions-on-the-evm%5C%22%3EBefore%20Celebrating%20%E2%80%98Remote%20Voting%E2%80%99%2C%20EC%20Should%20Address%20Longstanding%20Questions%20on%20the%20EVM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20election%20and%20its%20results%20were%20challenged%20on%20the%20following%20grounds%20also%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20the%20constitution%20envisages%20elections%20as%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20formation%20of%20legislature%20and%20the%20consequent%20executive.%20The%20most%20significant%20function%20of%20elections%20is%20to%20establish%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20elected%20officials%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20citizens.%20That%20in%20order%20to%20uphold%20and%20preserve%20the%20sanctity%20of%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20undeniably%20imperative%20that%20election%20results%20are%20accurate.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20sufficient%20that%20election%20results%20are%20accurate%2C%20the%20public%20must%20also%20know%20that%20the%20results%20are%20accurate.%20The%20entire%20electoral%20process%20is%20damaged%20if%20elections%20are%20not%20credible%20even%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20demonstrable%20scam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20the%20discrepancies%20between%20the%20actual%20voter%20turnout%20and%20provisional%20data%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20significant%20and%20cannot%20be%20set%20aside%20without%20a%20satisfactory%20resolution%20of%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20the%20current%20statute%20has%20a%20procedure%20for%20resolution%20of%20a%20dispute%20through%20an%20election%20petition%20but%20no%20provision%20for%20resolution%20of%20the%20doubts%20arising%20out%20of%20discrepancies%20in%20very%20large%20number%20of%20constituencies%20all%20over%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20declaration%20of%20election%20results%20with%20alacrity%20should%20not%20be%20a%20priority%20at%20the%20altar%20of%20accuracy%20and%20integrity%20of%20elections.%20Several%20serious%20lapses%20can%20go%20unnoticed%20in%20the%20counting%20process%20in%20the%20rush%20to%20declare%20results%20and%20the%20winners.%20Conduct%20of%20Parliamentary%20elections%20in%20our%20country%20is%20a%20gigantic%20exercise%20spread%20over%20two-three%20months.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20announce%20accurate%20results%20great%20deliberation%20is%20required%2C%20hence%20to%20expect%20and%20want%20the%20counting%20process%20to%20be%20over%20in%20just%20few%20hours%20is%20not%20desirable.%20That%20this%20unwarranted%20urgency%20of%20concluding%20counting%20process%20on%20mere%20assumptions%20and%20conjectures%20shorn%20of%20the%20genuine%20authenticated%20data%20is%20a%20strictly%20flawed%20notion%20and%20therefore%20requires%20an%20immediate%20attention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20resolution%20of%20doubts%20and%20discrepancies%20in%20electoral%20results%20are%20as%20essential%20for%20a%20democracy%20as%20resolution%20of%20disputes%20relating%20to%20an%20election%20exercise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20petition%20also%20stated%20that%20even%20though%20the%20results%20for%20all%20constituencies%20were%20declared%20by%20the%20ECI%20on%20May%2023%2C%202019%2C%20the%20ECI%20itself%20admitted%20on%20June%201%2C%202019%20that%20the%20index%20forms%20of%20all%20542%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20are%20expected%20to%20reach%20them%20from%20Returning%20Officers%20%E2%80%9Cshortly%E2%80%9D.%20Thus%20it%20had%20admitted%20that%20up%20to%20June%201%2C%202019%20the%20ECI%20had%20not%20received%20the%20actual%20data%20and%20that%20the%20declaration%20of%20results%20was%20not%20based%20on%20data%20recorded%20by%20the%20Returning%20Officers.%20This%20is%20a%20fatal%20flaw%20that%20not%20only%20questions%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20election%20but%20also%20the%20very%20legality%20of%20the%20parliament%20constituted%20thereof.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20admitted%20the%20petition%20and%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20ECI.%20But%20till%20date%2C%20it%20has%20not%20seen%20the%20light%20of%20the%20day.%20It%20is%20equally%20shocking%20that%20even%20after%20nearly%20four%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20not%20provided%20the%20tally%20of%20EVM%20and%20VVPAT%20counts.%20So%20much%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20democracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20was%20the%20parliament%20election%2C%202019%2C%20manipulated%3F%20Your%20guess%20is%20as%20good%20as%20mine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fm-g-devasahayam-2%5C%22%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20