%20for%20borrowers%20on%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20groups%20said%20in%20their%20complaint%20that%20the%20relief%20was%20an%20overreach%20of%20authority.%20They%20also%20said%20that%2C%20as%20nonprofits%2C%20it%20also%20undermined%20their%20recruiting%20efforts%20through%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program%2C%20which%20forgives%20student%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Education%20Department%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20lawsuit%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20from%20right%20wing%20special%20interests%20to%20keep%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20borrowers%20in%20debt%2C%20even%20though%20these%20borrowers%20have%20earned%20the%20forgiveness%20that%20is%20promised%20through%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans.%C2%A0%C2%A0We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20back%20down%20or%20give%20an%20inch%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20defending%20working%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20days%20later%2C%20a%20separate%20debt%20relief%20measure%20got%20blocked%20in%20court.%20On%20August%207%2C%20a%20three-judge%20panel%20consisting%20of%20Trump%20and%20Reagan%20appointees%20in%20the%20Fifth%20Circuit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-borrower-defense-rules-fifth-circuit-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Eblocked%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Education%20Department's%20new%20rules%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-just-got-easier-defrauded-borrowers-debt-relief-2023-2%5C%22%3Emake%20it%20easier%20for%20borrowers%20who%20say%20they%20were%20defrauded%20by%20the%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20attended%20to%20discharge%20their%20debt.%20The%20new%20rules%20concerned%20the%20process%20known%20as%20borrower%20defense%2C%20and%20they%20would%20create%20a%20more%20streamlined%20application%20and%20expand%20the%20types%20of%20school%20misconduct%20that%20would%20qual