li%3EPamela%20Voss%20and%20her%20husband%20own%20a%20geodesic%20dome%20home%20on%2015%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20eastern%20Texas.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20a%20dome%20home%20is%20worth%20it%20for%20the%20unique%20living%20space%20and%20energy%20efficiency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20future%20dome%20homeowners%20should%20carefully%20research%20banks%20and%20insurance%2C%20Voss%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20series%20of%20conversations%20with%20Pamela%20Voss%2C%20who%20has%20lived%20in%20a%20dome%20home%20in%20Texas%20since%202021.%20All%20costs%20mentioned%20have%20been%20verified%20by%20Insider.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20first%20walked%20into%20our%204%2C000%20square-foot%20Texas%20dome%20home%20in%20spring%202021%2C%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%3A%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%20this%20is%20so%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20uniqueness%20of%20the%20home%20and%20our%20desire%20to%20live%20in%20a%20more%20rural%20area%20drew%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20to%20the%20home.%20Plus%2C%20geodesic%20dome%20homes%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20are%20constructed%20out%20of%20triangle-shaped%20pieces%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20cost%20nearly%20as%20much%20as%20a%20traditional%20home%20these%20days%2C%20hold%20their%20value%20well%2C%20and%20will%20last%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we've%20faced%20some%20obstacles%20to%20financing%20and%20insuring%20our%20energy-efficient%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdome-home-homeowners-say-structures-natural-disaster-resistant-energy-efficient-2023-8%5C%22%3Eweather-proof%20dome%20home.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Here%20are%20my%20top%20three%20tips%20for%20people%20looking%20to%20live%20in%20a%20dome%20home%20like%20ours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20a%20geodesic%20dome%20ceiling.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cab0d4ce6977001984c4e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVisitors%20often%20say%20Voss'%20home%20looks%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomfortable%20museum.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Pamela%20Voss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EFind%20a%20local%20mortgage%20lender%20willing%20to%20finance%20a%20dome%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20your%20homework%20on%20mortgage%20lenders%20upfront.%20Don't%20go%20with%20the%20national%2C%20big-box%20mortgage%20companies.%20Stay%20local%2C%20and%20call%20the%20bank%20ahead%20of%20time%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20can%20provide%20a%20mortgage%20on%20a%20geodesic%20dome%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20learned%20this%20just%20weeks%20before%20we%20closed%20on%20the%20house%2C%20which%20we%20bought%20for%20about%20%24450%2C000.%20We%20found%20out%20the%20big%20national%20mortgage%20companies%20wouldn't%20loan%20to%20us%20because%20there%20were%20no%20nearby%20comps%2C%20which%20are%20comparable%20properties%20in%20a%20similar%20area%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20comparatively%20determine%20the%20value%20of%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20banks%20we%20spoke%20to%20told%20us%20we%20had%20to%20have%20three%20comps%20that%20have%20been%20sold%20in%20the%20same%20county%20within%20the%20past%2012%20months.%20Dome%20homes%20in%20our%20area%20aren't%20prevalent%20enough%20to%20have%20comps%2C%20so%20we%20fought%20back%20and%20asked%20if%20they%20could%20use%20traditional%20homes%20of%20a%20comparable%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20banks%20told%20us%20that%20a%20dome%20is%20in%20its%20own%20category%20of%20structure%2C%20so%20they%20could%20not%20compare%20a%20dome%20home%20with%20a%20regular%20single-family%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20we%20went%20to%20a%20local%20bank%20and%20were%20able%20to%20fast-track%20the%20approval%20process.%20Our%20interest%20rate%20was%20almost%20double%20what%20the%20big%20box%20company%20would've%20given%20us.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20do%20a%20balloon%20mortgage%2C%20which%20is%20a%20special%20type%20of%20loan%20that%20gives%20buyers%20an%20initial%20period%20of%20low%20or%20zero-dollar%20payments.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20period%2C%20the%20buyer%20has%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20full%20balance%20in%20a%20lump%20sum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20very%20fortunate%20that%20we%20sold%20our%20previous%20home%20and%20had%20a%20very%20sizable%20downpayment.%20After%20all%20that%2C%20our%20mortgage%20on%20the%20%24450%2C000%20home%20was%20only%20about%20%24100%2C000%2C%20which%20we%20paid%20back%20after%20our%20initial%20two-year%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20the%20same%20headache%20we%20went%20through%2C%20find%20a%20small%20company.%20They%20can%20do%20some%20more%20clever%2C%20unique%20things%20with%20your%20loan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHire%20a%20trustworthy%20inspector%20who%20can%20ensure%20the%20dome%20home%20is%20leak-proof%20and%20safe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20you've%20found%20a%20way%20to%20finance%20your%20dome%20home%2C%20find%20a%20good%20inspector%2C%20because%20if%20you're%20buying%20a%20previously-owned%20dome%20home%2C%20you%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20it%20was%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20a%20good%20inspector%20so%20that%20you're%20not%20buying%20a%20house%20that%20has%20existing%20water%20damage%2C%20forcing%20you%20to%20replace%20all%20the%20wood.%20Sometimes%2C%20skylights%20and%20windows%20in%20dome%20homes%20can%20leak%20at%20the%20edges%20because%20of%20how%20they%20are%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20many%20dome%20homes%20also%20need%20a%20cupola%2C%20which%20is%20a%20gazebo-like%20structure%20at%20the%20highest%20point%20of%20the%20dome.%20These%20are%20built%20to%20prevent%20water%20from%20leaking%20onto%20the%20roof%20and%20then%20down%20all%20the%20angles%20and%20getting%20into%20the%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20fortunate%20to%20have%20a%20home%20built%20by%20an%20engineer%2C%20so%20there%20were%20no%20corners%20cut.%20For%20instance%2C%20our%20insulation%20is%20six%20inches%20thicker%20than%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20for%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20staircase%20going%20to%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20dome%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d6a3b75e5d5a00195cb5c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVoss'%204%2C000%20square%20foot%20dome%20home%20initially%20cost%20about%20%24450%2C000.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Pamela%20Voss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ELook%20for%20home%20insurance%20companies%20that%20aren't%20afraid%20of%20insuring%20a%20unique%20structure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20homeowner's%20insurance%20initially%20went%20sky-high%20when%20we%20bought%20our%20dome%20home%2C%20with%20national%20companies%20quoting%20us%20about%20%244%2C500%20a%20year.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20some%20home%20insurance%20companies%20are%20afraid%20of%20domes%20because%20they're%20unfamiliar%20with%20them.%20Some%20companies%20were%20just%20concerned%20about%20the%20roof%2C%20or%20the%20skylights%20leaking.%20One%20company%20even%20told%20us%20that%20the%20trees%20on%20our%20property%20were%20so%20tall%20that%20it%20was%20a%20hazard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20experience%20taught%20me%20to%20find%20insurance%20companies%20that%20insure%20unique%20structures.%20Now%2C%20I%20use%20the%20Texas%20Farm%20Bureau%2C%20where%20I%20only%20pay%20%243%2C123%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20several%20hundred%20dollars%20lower%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nerdwallet.com%2Farticle%2Finsurance%2Fhome-insurance-texas%5C%22%3Estate%20average%20of%20%243%2C875.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAfter%20you%20take%20these%20steps%2C%20you%20can%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20dome's%20safety%20and%20energy%20efficiency.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGeodesic%20dome%20homes%20like%20ours%20are%20incredibly%20sturdy.%20They%20can%20withstand%20extreme%20weather%20events%20like%20tornadoes%20pretty%20well.%20Because%20we%20live%20in%20Texas%2C%20this%20is%20really%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20despite%20navigating%20a%20complicated%20mortgage%20and%20insurance%20process%2C%20we've%20actually%20saved%20money.%20Our%20energy%20bill%20is%20nearly%2030%25%20less%20than%20our%20previous%20home.%20During%20the%20hot%20summer%20months%20we%20pay%20about%20%24400%2C%20and%20in%20the%20spring%20and%20fall%20our%20bill%20is%20between%20%24200-%24300.%20That's%20thanks%20to%20the%20dome%20shape%2C%20which%20is%20incredibly%20energy-efficient.%20We%20need%20just%20one%20AC%20unit%20for%20the%20entire%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20the%20home%20is%20a%20huge%20selling%20point.%20The%20dome%20home%20has%20been%20a%20super%20fun%20decorating%20challenge%20for%20me.%20Multiple%20people%20have%20even%20said%20our%20home%20looks%20like%20a%20comfortable%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisitors%20always%20come%20in%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20my%20God%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20it%20was%20gonna%20look%20like%20this%20inside.%20This%20is%20so%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-live-in-a-dome-tips-buying-mortgage-insurance-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691924401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d6a2b01f51cc0019683766%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-live-in-a-dome-tips-buying-mortgage-insurance-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20important%20to%20do%20your%20homework%20on%20the%20best%20mortgage%20lenders%2C%20home%20insurance%20companies%2C%20and%20inspectors%20before%20buying%20a%20dome%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22khawkinson%40insider.com%20(Katie%20