0his%20first%20title%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia%20club%20Al-Nassr.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fcristiano-ronaldo-shatters-iconic-record-en-route-clinching-first-trophy-with-al-nassr-4294162%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fcristiano-ronaldo-shatters-iconic-record-en-route-clinching-first-trophy-with-al-nassr-4294162%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fcristiano-ronaldo-shatters-iconic-record-en-route-clinching-first-trophy-with-al-nassr-4294162%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20World%20Discovered%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Got%20the%20Taste%20for%20%E2%80%93%20Scotch%20Whiskey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13162422%2F14179521094_2c1b5c942a_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EScotch%20whiskey%20exports%20grew%20from%20%C2%A34.51%20billion%20in%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scotch-whisky.org.uk%2Fnewsroom%2Fscotch-whisky-exports-2022%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20more%20than%20%C2%A36%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20while%20separate%20government%20figures%20showed%20a%2025%25%20sales%20increase%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20the%20biggest%20for%20any%20UK%20manufactured%20product%20except%20aircraft%20parts.%20Such%20impressive%20growth%20shows%20how%20the%20industry%20has%20cultivated%20its%20image%2C%20appeal%20and%20supply%20networks%20over%20200%20years%2C%20withstanding%20pandemics%2C%20trade%20wars%20and%20even%20world%20wars%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20why%20Scotch%20whiskey%20has%20managed%20to%20keep%20its%20global%20popularity%20over%20a%20long%20time%20period%20is%20one%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gla.ac.uk%2Fschools%2Fbusiness%2Fstaff%2Fniallmackenzie%2F%23publications%2Cbooksections%5C%22%3Eresearching%20for%20several%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Like%20a%20good%20Scotch%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20complex%20and%20requires%20time%20to%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScotch%20whiskey%20producers%20have%20long%20looked%20overseas%20to%20sell%20their%20product.%20The%20UK%20domestic%20market%20is%20not%20and%20never%20has%20been%20big%20enough%20to%20meet%20their%20aspirations%20for%20growth.%20Some%20of%20the%20earliest%20records%20of%20Scotch%20being%20exported%20date%20to%201839%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ardbegproject.com%2Fardbeg-in-usa.shtml%5C%22%3Eadverts%20for%20Ardbeg%20Scotch%20from%20Islay%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%20appearing%20in%20New%20York%20publications%20around%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20not%20until%20later%20in%20the%2019th%20century%20that%20the%20Scotch%20whiskey%20industry%20really%20began%20to%20focus%20on%20going%20global.%20In%20the%20mid%201800s%2C%20the%20government%20relaxed%20regulations%20regarding%20blending.%20Previously%20producers%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20mix%20or%20blend%20their%20individual%20whiskies%2C%20which%20were%20often%20raw%20and%20inconsistent.%20After%20the%20rules%20changed%2C%20the%20industry%20could%20produce%20a%20consistent%20and%20wide%20variety%20of%20flavours%20to%20suit%20different%20palates%2C%20giving%20whiskey%20the%20opportunity%20to%20appeal%20more%20broadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombined%20with%20already%20established%20global%20trade%20routes%20out%20of%20the%20UK%2C%20Scotch%20whiskey%20blenders%20such%20as%20Dewar%E2%80%99s%2C%20Buchanan%E2%80%99s%20and%20Johnnie%20Walker%20were%20able%20to%20grow%20their%20businesses%20domestically%20and%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20global%20taste%20for%20whiskey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20blended%20Scotch%20whiskey%20makes%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scotch-whisky.org.uk%2Fnewsroom%2Fscotch-whisky-exports-2022%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20majority%20(59%25)%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20exports%20by%20value.%20Blended%20Scotch%20also%20achieved%20the%20biggest%20increase%20in%20exports%20in%20the%20last%20year.%20It%20grew%20by%2043%25%2C%20fuelling%20the%20overall%20Scotch%20export%20value%20increase%20of%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20and%20China%20have%20emerged%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20key%20destinations%2C%20the%20early%20export%20markets%20established%20by%20Scotch%20producers%20such%20as%20the%20US%2C%20France%2C%20South%20America%2C%20and%20Asian%20countries%20including%20Singapore%20and%20Taiwan%2C%20are%20still%20the%20principal%20destinations%20for%20Scotch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20has%20been%20subject%20to%20close%20attention%20from%20the%20Westminster%20government%20in%20the%20form%20of%20regulation%20and%20taxation%20for%20the%20past%20200%20years%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scotch-whisky.org.uk%2Fdiscover%2Fstory-of-scotch%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DIn%25201823%2520the%2520Excise%2520Act%2Cper%2520gallon%2520of%2520proof%2520spirithave%5C%22%3EExcise%20Act%20of%201823%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20has%20encouraged%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20overseas%20focus.%20Tariffs%20and%20outright%20bans%20such%20as%20US%20prohibition%20from%201920-1933%20did%20little%20to%20dampen%20thirst%20for%20the%20spirit.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20prohibition%2C%20the%20industry%20used%20all%20manner%20of%20means%20to%20get%20Scotch%20into%20the%20US%20including%20rum%20runners%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20and%20mobster%20ties%20through%20Canada%20%E2%80%93%20most%20recently%20depicted%20in%20the%20TV%20show%20Peaky%20Blinders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20since%20the%20early%2020th%20century%2C%20the%20UK%20government%20has%20recognised%20and%20pushed%20the%20export%20value%20of%20Scotch%20as%20a%20benefit%20to%20the%20economy.%20Winston%20Churchill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpanache%2Fwinston-churchills-painting-of-his-favourite-whisky-goes-on-sale-expected-to-fetch-330k%2Farticleshow%2F79147333.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ea%20well-known%20Scotch%20drinker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recognised%20its%20dollar-earning%20value%20during%20the%20second%20world%20war%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscotchwhisky.com%2Fmagazine%2Ffamous-whisky-drinkers%2F9866%2Fsir-winston-churchill%2F%5C%22%3Ea%201945%20government%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20stating%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20no%20account%20reduce%20the%20barley%20for%20whiskey.%20This%20takes%20years%20to%20mature%20and%20is%20an%20invaluable%20export%20%E2%80%A6%20Having%20regard%20to%20all%20our%20other%20difficulties%20about%20export%2C%20it%20would%20be%20most%20improvident%20not%20to%20preserve%20this%20characteristic%20British%20element%20of%20ascendancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20focus%20on%20exports%20damaged%20the%20domestic%20trade.%20After%20US%20prohibition%20and%20the%20second%20world%20war%2C%20global%20Scotch%20whiskey%20exports%20grew%20as%20a%20proportion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00076791.2022.2085251%5C%22%3Efrom%2050%25%20of%20total%20UK%20production%20in%201939%20to%2075%25%20by%201954%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20industry%20has%20since%20faced%20various%20challenges%20in%20international%20markets%2C%20but%20has%20still%20continued%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERising%20to%20the%20challenge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScotch%20exports%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-scotland-scotland-business-36302482%5C%22%3Eslower%20in%20recent%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20combined%20effects%20of%20free%20movement%20(affecting%20the%20important%20duty-free%20market%20for%20Scotch)%20and%20trade%20restrictions%20arising%20from%20the%20global%20pandemic%2C%20Brexit%20and%20the%20introduction%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedrinksbusiness.com%2F2023%2F07%2Findia-reconsiders-tariffs-on-imports-of-bulk-whisky%2F%5C%22%3Ehigh%20tariffs%20in%20key%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20the%20US%20and%20India.%20But%20whiskey%20producers%20have%20clearly%20learned%20lessons%20from%20a%20long%20history%20of%20responding%20to%20global%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20quickly%20adapted%20by%20focusing%20on%20quality%20and%20luxury%20and%20pushing%20new%20products.%20The%20emergence%20of%20single%20malts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00076791.2022.2085251%5C%22%3Eover%20the%20past%2030%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20distinct%20product%20in%20export%20markets%20is%20a%20good%20example%20of%20this.%20Prior%20to%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20single%20malt%20was%20a%20relatively%20niche%20product%20without%20significant%20reach%20into%20markets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00076791.2022.2085251%5C%22%3Eeither%20at%20home%20or%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%2C%20a%20global%20collapse%20in%20demand%20for%20blended%20Scotch%20led%20to%20an%20overstocking%20of%20single%20malt%20%E2%80%9Cfillings%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ingredients%20for%20blended%20Scotch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20used%20marketing%2C%20branding%20and%20distribution%20strategies%20to%20turn%20this%20overstock%20into%20a%20luxury%20product%20by%20building%20the%20perception%20of%20scarcity%2C%20and%20value%20in%20age%20and%20provenance.%20Single%20malts%20have%20since%20grown%20to%20comprise%20around%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20value%20of%20Scotch%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20Scotch%20whiskey%20industry%E2%80%99s%20recent%20success%20in%20export%20growth%20did%20not%20happen%20overnight.%20It%20has%20taken%20a%20long%20time%20to%20develop%20and%20mature.%20Much%20like%20a%20good%20Scotch%20whiskey.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F210595%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENiall%20G%20MacKenzie%2C%20Professor%20of%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20Business%20History%2C%20University%20of%20Glasgow.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fhow-canny-marketing-and-strong-supply-links-gave-the-world-a-taste-for-scotch-whisky-210595%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691924184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13162422%2F14179521094_2c1b5c942a_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Fhow-the-world-discovered-and-got-the-taste-for-scotch-whiskey%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Like%20a%20good%20Scotch%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20complex%20and%20requires%20time%20to%20understand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Fhow-the-world-discovered-and-got-the-taste-for-scotch-whiskey%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Kohli%20wanted%20to%20win%2C%20but%20he%20was%E2%80%A6'%3A%20Ex-Pak%20player%20alleges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691923870000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102696907%2Cimgsize-38606.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fvirat-kohli-wanted-to-win-but-he-was-former-pakistan-player-alleges%2Farticleshow%2F102696908.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20owns%20the%20plethora%20of%20records%20in%20international%20cricket%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20his%20captaincy%20an%20ICC%20trophy%20eluded%20him.%20However%2C%20he%20led%20the%20team%20to%20numerous%20victories%2C%20under%20his%20captaincy%2C%20India%20achieved%20their%20first-ever%20Test%20series%20victory%20in%20Australia%20during%20the%202018-2019%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah's%20%5C%22Old%20Wine%20In%20Old%20Bottle%5C%22%20Swipe%20At%20Opposition%20Alliance%20INDIA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Sunday%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20likening%20it%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bold%20wine%20in%20old%20bottle%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20it%20was%20a%20group%20of%20leaders%20involved%20in%20corruption%20worth%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20attacked%20the%20opposition%20Congress%2C%20saying%20during%20its%20rule%2C%20India's%20economy%20did%20not%20go%20beyond%20the%2011th%20rank%20in%20the%20world%2C%20while%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20it%20to%20the%205th%20position%20in%20one%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20addressing%20a%20gathering%20after%20laying%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20a%20regional%20centre%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Guard%20(NSG)%20in%20Mansa%20town%20in%20Gujarat's%20Gandhinagar%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20a%20group%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%20have%20come%20together%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20to%20take%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20UPA%20and%20Congress%20are%20a%20group%20of%20leaders%20involved%20in%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20crore%20corruption.%20They%20have%20now%20changed%20their%20name%2C%20haven't%20they%3F%20But%20you%20must%20refer%20to%20them%20as%20UPA...Who%20will%20vote%20for%20those%20who%20have%20committed%20a%20scam%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20crore%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHaven't%20you%20heard%20the%20saying%3A%20'Old%20wine%20in%20a%20new%20bottle'.%20But%20here%20both%20the%20bottle%20and%20the%20wine%20are%20old.%20So%2C%20do%20not%20get%20cheated.%20Under%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20return%20to%20power%20with%20full%20majority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20further%20said%20many%20of%20us%20have%20not%20seen%20the%20country's%20struggle%20for%20independence%20and%20have%20not%20got%20the%20opportunity%20to%20die%20for%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20say%20had%20they%20been%20there%2C%20they%20would%20have%20sacrificed%20their%20life%20for%20the%20nation.%20We%20do%20not%20need%20to%20sacrifice%20our%20life%20for%20the%20nation%2C%20but%20nobody%20can%20stop%20us%20from%20living%20for%20the%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20us%20raise%20five%20children%2C%20starting%20from%20our%20home%2C%20who%20are%20filled%20to%20the%20brim%20with%20patriotism%2C%20whose%20entire%20life%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20country.%20Let%20us%20raise%20five%20children%20who%20live%20for%20our%20language%2C%20literature%2C%20culture%2C%20village%2C%20state%20and%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20also%20said%20that%20while%20he%20is%20not%20against%20English%20as%20a%20language%2C%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20keep%20the%20Gujarati%20language%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20student%20does%20not%20learn%20Gujarati%2C%20he%20will%20not%20recognise%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20the%20country.%20And%20if%20he%20does%20not%20recognise%20the%20country%2C%20he%20will%20never%20do%20anything%20good%20for%20it.%20If%20we%20do%20not%20introduce%20our%20children%20to%20the%2015%2C000%20years'%20old%20culture%20of%20our%20country%2C%20then%20we%20shall%20be%20responsible%20for%20endangering%20our%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20shown%20the%20path%20to%20the%20world%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20and%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20help%20create%20an%20India%20which%20is%20on%20top%20in%20fields%20ranging%20from%20education%2C%20space%2C%20security%20and%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691923680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fcjbni0u_amit-shah-1200_625x300_13_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shahs-old-wine-in-old-bottle-swipe-at-opposition-alliance-india-4294356%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Sunday%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20likening%20it%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bold%20wine%20in%20old%20bottle%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20it%20was%20a%20group%20of%20leaders%20involved%20in%20corruption%20worth%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shahs-old-wine-in-old-bottle-swipe-at-opposition-alliance-india-4294356%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shahs-old-wine-in-old-bottle-swipe-at-opposition-alliance-india-4294356%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shahs-old-wine-in-old-bottle-swipe-at-opposition-alliance-india-4294356%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Ahead%20of%20Polls%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Pitches%20Ravidas%20Against%20Mughals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13160642%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-4.06.29-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20August%2012%20remembered%20medieval-era%20Bhakti%20poet%20Sant%20Ravidas%20for%20his%20%E2%80%9Ccourage%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpatriotism%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-the-ichr-is-inventing-history-under-the-modi-government%5C%22%3Eduring%20the%20Mughal%20period%20when%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Modi%2C%20Indian%20society%20grappled%20with%20%E2%80%9Cassaults%20on%20its%20faith%E2%80%9D%20and%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cerase%20its%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20made%20the%20remarks%20after%20launching%20several%20projects%20in%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20It%20included%20him%20laying%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20a%20memorial%20dedicated%20to%20Ravidas%2C%20a%20poet%20and%20philosopher%20who%20stood%20against%20institutionalised%20caste%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20performed%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhoomi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Epujan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(rituals%20for%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20grounds)%20for%20the%20Sant%20Shiromani%20Gurudev%20Shri%20Ravidas%20ji%20Memorial%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Sagar%2C%20a%20district%20located%20in%20the%20Bundelkhand%20region%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavidas%20is%20revered%20by%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Dalits%2C%20especially%20in%20northern%20states%20such%20as%20Punjab%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20Bundelkhand%20region%20of%20MP%2C%20consisting%20of%20seven%20districts%2C%20has%20a%20Dalit%20population%20much%20above%20the%20state%20average%20of%2015.6%25%20(as%20per%20the%202011%20Census).%20Thus%20the%20building%20pf%20memorials%20and%20the%20promotion%20of%20popular%20Dalit%20icons%20has%20over%20the%20years%20emerged%20as%20a%20strategy%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20to%20woo%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sagar%2C%20which%20has%20a%20Dalit%20population%20of%20over%2021%25%2C%20Modi%20evoked%20a%20popular%20couplet%20of%20Ravidas%20which%20speaks%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eparadheenta%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20dependence%20and%20connected%20it%20with%20present%20India%E2%80%99s%20spirit%20of%20rejecting%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmentality%20of%20slavery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EParadheenta%20paap%20hai%2C%20jaan%20lehu%20re%20meet.%20Raidas%20paradheen%20sau%2C%20kaun%20kare%20hain%20preet%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%20translated%2C%20it%20means%3A%20dependency%20is%20a%20big%20sin%20and%20those%20who%20accept%20it%20and%20do%20not%20take%20a%20stand%20against%20it%20are%20not%20loved%20by%20anybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20started%20by%20describing%20the%20Mughal%20period%20as%20one%20when%20the%20Indian%20society%20faced%20%E2%80%9Cinstability%2C%20persecution%20and%20oppression.%E2%80%9D%20Even%20during%20those%20days%2C%20Modi%20said%2C%20Ravidas%20tried%20to%20awaken%20the%20society%20and%20teach%20it%20how%20to%20fight%20against%20its%20evil%20practices%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20were%20assaults%20on%20our%20faith%2C%20when%20restrictions%20were%20being%20imposed%20on%20us%20to%20erase%20our%20identity%2C%20even%20in%20those%20days%20%E2%80%93%20during%20the%20Mughal-period%20%E2%80%93%20look%20at%20the%20courage%20and%20patriotism%20with%20which%20Ravidas%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20%5Bthe%20couplet%5D%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20Ravidas%E2%80%99s%20teachings%20had%20provided%20the%20society%20with%20the%20strength%20to%20fight%20oppression%20and%20that%20even%20Maratha%20ruler%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20had%20used%20it%20as%20an%20inspiration%20to%20lay%20the%20foundation%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindavi%20Swarajya%E2%80%9D%20or%20self-rule%20of%20Indian%20people.%20The%20spirit%20continued%20to%20flow%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20lakhs%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20during%20the%201857%20struggle%20against%20the%20British%20and%20today%2C%20the%20nation%20was%20moving%20forward%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20the%20same%20spirit%20of%20liberation%20and%20rejecting%20the%20mentality%20of%20slavery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20event%2C%20Modi%20elaborated%20on%20some%20schemes%20that%20had%20benefitted%20people%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20communities.%E2%80%9D%20These%20groups%20have%20been%20the%20biggest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20run%20by%20the%20government%20for%20the%20poor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202018%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20secured%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20BJP%20and%20managed%20to%20form%20a%20government%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20four%20independent%20winners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202020%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20by%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20toppled%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government%20after%20almost%20two%20dozen%20Congress%20MLAs%20resigned%20and%20shifted%20loyalty%20to%20the%20saffron%20party.%20Barring%20the%20one-year%20stint%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20in%20between%2C%20Chouhan%20has%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20state%20for%20almost%20last%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20Chouhan%20are%20battling%20fatigue%20and%20possible%20anti-incumbency%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20would%20need%20to%20perform%20reasonably%20better%20in%20regions%20such%20as%20Bundelkhand%20where%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20two%20Uttar%20Pradesh-based%20parties%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20had%20a%20decent%20run%20in%20the%20last%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ravidas%20memorial%20would%20be%20constructed%20in%20an%20area%20of%20more%20than%2011.25%20acres%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore.%20It%20will%20include%20an%20art%20museum%20and%20a%20gallery%20to%20showcase%20his%20life%2C%20phil