m%20by%20the%20preliminary%20inquiry.%20He%20has%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20Lokayukta%20before%20August%2021%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20explained%20his%20position%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20your%20view%2C%20what%20are%20the%20origins%20of%20this%20fraught%20issue%20over%20land%20acquisition%20in%20Manipur%20for%20the%20Railways%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process%20at%20Marangjing%20in%20Manipur%20started%20in%202010-11%2C%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20interference%20whatsoever%20from%20the%20present%20petitioners%20who%20now%20claim%20that%20the%20entire%20land%20of%20the%20village%20is%20a%20common%20land.%20The%20earlier%20phase%20of%20compensation%20was%20paid%20to%20the%20concerned%20land%20owners.%20If%2C%20as%20per%20the%20claim%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20land%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20is%20a%20common%20village%20property%20and%20that%20there%20is%20no%20individual%20land%20owner%2C%20I%20think%20there%20would%20be%20an%20uproar%20everywhere%20else%20across%20the%20hill%20districts%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20personally%20handled%20compensation%20matters%20in%20the%20area%20of%20Tamenglong%20and%20land%20acquired%20for%20various%20projects%20have%20been%20under%20the%20name%20of%20the%20land%20owners.%20Just%20to%20turn%20it%20in%20their%20favour%2C%20they%20cannot%20suddenly%20change%20the%20land%20holding%20systems%20of%20the%20tribals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20issue%20has%20its%20origins%20in%202014-15%2C%20when%20the%20Railways%20sent%20a%20requirement%20for%20over%20137%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20and%20around%20Makhuam-Kharam%20Pallen-Pungmuon%20villages%20area.%20When%20the%20District%20Collector%20(DC)%20at%20that%20time%20deputed%20the%20concerned%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESub%20Divisional%20Officer%3C%2Fspan%3E%20(SDO)%20of%20Tamenglong%20to%20do%20field%20survey%2C%20there%20was%20an%20opposition%2C%20too%2C%20from%20this%20group%20of%20villagers%20led%20by%20Gongchalung%20and%20his%20party%20against%20the%20Pungmoun%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20these%20pressures%20to%20stop%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process%2C%20the%20then%20DC%20sent%20the%20requirements%20of%20this%20land%20to%20the%20Revenue%20Department%2C%20Government%20of%20Manipur%2C%20indicating%20clearly%20under%20whose%20village%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20land%20falls.%20It%20may%20clearly%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20letter%20that%20the%20portion%20of%2037%20acres%20was%20under%20Marangjing%20village%2C%2022%20acres%20disputed%20while%2077%20acres%20was%20under%20the%20Pungmuon%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20follow%20up%20of%20the%20field%20report%2C%20the%20then%20DC%2C%20Ngaranchan%20Luikham%2C%20forwarded%20the%20entire%20evaluation%20along%20with%20financial%20implications%20to%20the%20concerned%20authorities%20along%20with%20the%20field%20survey%20reports%2C%20with%20names%20of%20the%20land%20owner%20in%20the%20case%20of%2037%20and%2077%20acres%20while%20that%20of%2022%20acres%20as%20disputed.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20compensation%20amount%20for%2022%20acres%2C%20which%20has%20been%20recorded%20as%20disputed%2C%20still%20is%20not%20awarded%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20not%20like%20to%20go%20into%20the%20process%20of%20the%20land%20acquisition%20because%20this%20would%20mean%20undermining%20the%20acts%20of%20former%20DCs%20who%2C%20in%20all%20their%20wisdom%2C%20had%20carried%20out%20the%20entire%20process%20judiciously%20following%20all%20laid%20down%20rules%20and%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Marangjing%20village%20had%20the%20habit%20of%20taking%20law%20and%20order%20in%20their%20own%20hands%20by%20burning%20down%20vehicles%20and%20machinery%20if%20anything%20goes%20against%20their%20favour.%20When%20they%20lost%20the%20case%20on%20June%2016%2C%202017%2C%20it%20was%20the%20same%3B%20things%20went%20out%20of%20control%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20damage%20of%20several%20properties%20of%20both%20public%20and%20private%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maringjing%20village%20being%20a%20big%20village%20always%20wants%20to%20superimpose%20their%20authority%20over%20smaller%20villages%20like%20Pungmoun%2C%20despite%20having%20lost%20almost%20all%20the%20cases%20they%20themselves%20have%20filed.%20At%20any%20given%20instances%2C%20they%20would%20collect%20all%20the%20keys%20to%20the%20machines%20and%20immediately%20halt%20the%20work%20within%20their%20village%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20am%20not%20wrong%2C%20theirs%20is%20the%20only%20village%20which%20had%20expelled%20several%20families%20of%20its%20own%20native%20villagers%20for%20supporting%20the%20order%20of%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20supporting%20the%20Railway%20works%2C%20after%20their%20houses%20being%20totally%20ransacked%20and%20destroyed%20by%20their%20own%20villagers.%20These%20families%20now%20live%20in%20and%20around%20the%20Imphal%20area%20in%20other%20lands%2C%20unable%20to%20come%20back%20and%20settle%20in%20their%20own%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114421%2Fimage-1215.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22861%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114421%2Fimage-1215.png%20608w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114421%2Fimage-1215-300x209.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667850%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHouse%20of%20Mr.%20Gaijinlung%20Kahmei%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20land%20owners%20of%20Makhuam%20village%20%E2%80%93%20being%20destroyed%20for%20supporting%20the%20government%20and%20court%E2%80%99s%20verdict.%20He%20has%20since%20been%20expelled%20from%20his%20own%20village%20and%20is%20now%20living%20in%20the%20Imphal%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114556%2Fimage-1216.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114556%2Fimage-1216.png%20781w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114556%2Fimage-1216-300x160.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667851%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22524%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELandowners%20of%20Marangjing%20village%20in%20support%20of%20Railway%20work%20despite%20bandh%20by%20on%20the%20work%20by%20their%20own%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20complainants%20before%20the%20Manipur%20Lokayukta%20accuse%20you%20of%20having%20%E2%80%98siphoned%20off%E2%80%99%20funds%2C%20what%20is%20your%20position%20on%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20same%20complainants%2C%20having%20lost%20this%20case%20at%20the%20DC%20office%20before%20my%20arrival%2C%20opposed%20the%20survey%20report%20and%20filed%20various%20cases%20in%20both%20the%20Civil%20Judge%20Senior%20Division%20Tamenglong%20and%20the%20District%20Judge%20Imphal%20West.%20According%20to%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%202013%2C%20the%20District%20Judge%20is%20the%20final%20authority%20for%20reference%20in%20Land%20Acquisition%20Matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20now%20taken%20up%20this%20matter%20with%20the%20Lokayukta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20really%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20many%20more%20courts%20they%20intend%20to%20take%20up%20on%20this%20case.%20One%20thing%20to%20be%20observed%20about%20the%20petitioners%20is%20that%20they%20will%20end%20up%20criticising%20the%20institution%20where%20they%20themselves%20have%20taken%20the%20matter%20for%20justice.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20cases%20which%20they%20lost%20in%20the%20court%20of%C2%A0%20Civil%20Judge%20(Senior%20Division)%20Tamenglong%2C%20they%20had%20even%20accused%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Court%20of%20having%20working%20hand%20in%20glove%20%5Bor%20colluding%5D%20with%20the%20office%20of%20Deputy%20Commissioner%2C%20%5Balleging%5D%20knowing%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20judgement%20beforehand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20complaints%20they%20had%20put%20forth%20in%20the%20Lokayukta%20against%20the%20officer.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20the%20Maranging%20village%20be%20prosecuted%20for%20defaming%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20civil%20court%3F%20If%20they%20have%20no%20faith%20in%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Court%2C%20why%20did%20they%20as%20a%20petitioner%20take%20up%20this%20case%3F%20All%20of%20these%20remain%20to%20be%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20in%20the%20court%20of%20the%20District%20Judge%2C%20Imphal%20West%2C%20they%20were%20the%20petitioners%20and%20lost%20the%20case%20again.%20They%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20judgment%20as%20it%20went%20against%20their%20favour.%20In%20view%20of%20all%20these%20precedents%2C%20tomorrow%20if%20the%20Lokayukta%20happens%20to%20conclude%20the%20matter%20against%20their%20favour%2C%20I%20would%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20they%20criticise%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%2C%20as%20a%20local%20of%20the%20district%2C%20believe%20in%20the%20best%20coexistence%20between%20the%20two%20villages.%20I%20knew%20that%20going%20through%20legal%20processes%20in%20the%20court%20of%20laws%2C%20enmity%20between%20the%20two%20villages%20would%20only%20be%20enhanced%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20that%20they%20would%20have%20to%20spend%20in%20the%20entire%20legal%20process%20would%20be%20too%20much%20and%20that%20this%20would%20never%20bring%20a%20permanent%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20reason%20with%20both%20the%20villages%20to%20settle%20the%20matters%20out%20of%20court.%20I%20had%20called%20%5Bthem%5D%20for%20a%20meeting%20in%20my%20office%2C%20discussed%20%5Bthe%20issue%5D%20with%20both%20the%20villages%20separately%20and%20also%20together%20on%20a%20common%20platform.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20reach%20a%20settlement%20outside%20the%20court%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20legal%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20on%20June%2014%2C%202017%20in%20my%20Office%20Chamber.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20both%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20village%20were%20very%20optimistic%20that%20one%20particular%20case%20(Civil%20Suit%208%20of%202015)%20in%20the%20court%20of%20Civil%20Judge%20Senior%20Division%20Tamenglong%20would%20be%20issued%20in%20their%20respective%20favours.%20They%20had%20not%20mentioned%20any%20other%20case%20apart%20from%20this%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20this%20was%20the%20only%20related%20case%20where%20the%20court%20had%20barred%20the%20DC%E2%80%99s%20office%20from%20awarding%20the%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20with%20the%20consensus%20of%20all%20the%20parties%20involved%2C%20the%20award%20was%20modified%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20above%20stated%20order.%20The%20modified%20order%20was%20issued%20on%20June%2015%2C%202017.%20On%20the%20June%2016%2C%20we%20received%20information%20from%20the%20other%20party%2C%20i.e.%20Lovejoy%20of%20Pungmuon%20village%20and%20Thuankunlung%2C%20that%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20dismissed.%20I%20clearly%20had%20told%20them%20that%20without%20a%20hard%20copy%2C%20I%20would%20not%20take%20any%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20some%20time%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20court%20order%20was%20brought%20to%20my%20office%20and%20after%20verifying%20the%20same%2C%20the%20award%20was%20given%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20Thuankulung%20and%20Lovejoy%2C%20as%20per%20all%20available%20records%20in%20the%20office%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20land%20survey%20records%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20these%20awards%20were%20given%20to%20villagers%20of%20Pungmuon%20village%2C%20through%20Lovejoy%2C%20and%20also%20to%20several%20farmers%20of%20Makhuam%20village%20who%20were%20cultivating%20the%20land%20belonging%20to%20Thuankulung%20of%20Marangjing%20village.%20Both%20of%20them%20had%20produced%20the%20concerned%20documents%20of%20the%20money%20being%20received%20by%20several%20farmers.%20You%20may%20like%20to%20verify%20this%20fact%20by%20going%20through%20all%20the%20APRs%20produced%20at%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20will%20be%20surprised%20that%20the%20same%20petitioners%2C%20who%20were%20leading%20several%20groups%20of%20youths%20and%20some%20women%20from%20the%20village%2C%20went%20on%20a%20rampage%20against%20the%20existing%20properties%2C%20and%20men%20of%20the%20various%20companies%20working%20day%20and%20night%20to%20complete%20the%20railway%20project.%20As%20this%20went%20uncontrollably%2Cto%20bring%20peace%20and%20normalcy%2C%20we%20called%20a%20meeting%20on%20July%205%2C%202017%2C%20and%20agreed%20that%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20these%20two%20individuals%20would%20be%20frozen%20till%20the%20time%20whatever%20case%20they%20claimed%20were%20pending%20in%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%20itself%2C%20they%20committed%20to%20give%20up%20all%20protests%20and%20other%20bans%20on%20the%20railway%20works.%20I%20assured%20them%20if%20in%20case%20they%20were%20proven%20right%20in%20the%20court%2C%20all%20the%20recovery%20would%20be%20done%20through%20my%20office.%20For%20the%20next%20eight%20Months%20till%20March%201%2C%202018%2C%20the%20accounts%20remained%20frozen.%20Does%20this%20mean%20I%20was%20scared%20of%20my%20own%20actions%20and%20trying%20to%20protect%20myself%3F%20Absolutely%20not.%20As%20someone%20who%20listens%20to%20their%20prayers%2C%20who%20believes%20in%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%2C%20waits%20for%20the%20final%20judgment%2C%20I%20acted%20only%20after%20the%20final%20judgment%20was%20given.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20judgment%2C%20paragraph%2023%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CSituated%20thus%2C%20I%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20prayer%20of%20the%20respondent%20no.%204%20to%20direct%20the%20collector%2C%20LA%2C%20Tamenglong%20to%20refer%20his%20claims%20to%20this%20authority%20cannot%20be%20entertained%20as%20there%20is%20no%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Collector%2C%20LA%2C%20Tamenglong%20to%20refer%20his%20claim%20to%20the%20authority%20since%20respondent%20No.4%20(Mr.Meithuaniung%20Gangmei%2C%20of%20Makhuam%20Village)%20did%20not%20file%20any%20application%20under%20section%2064(1)%20of%20RFCTLARR%20Act%2C%202013%20and%20that%20he%20has%20also%20failed%20to%20establish%20any%20prima%20facie%20right%20and%20title%20over%20the%20acquired%20lands%20mentioned%20in%20Sl.No.%202%20and%203.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20the%20frozen%20accounts%20were%20opened%20again%20after%20receiving%20the%20court%20order.%20Imagine%20if%20I%20had%20not%20unfrozen%20the%20accounts%2C%20I%20would%20have%20faced%20another%20contempt%20of%20court%20from%20the%20other%20party.%20Now%20they%20are%20questioning%20my%20action%20of%20why%20I%20froze%20the%20bank%20account%2C%20despite%20them%20being%20present%20for%20the%20meeting%20and%20agreeing%20on%20this%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20you%20tell%20the%20Lokayukta%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20exactly%20told%20the%20Lokayukta%20that%20no%20wrong%20has%20been%20committed%20on%20my%20part%20and%20that%20I%20had%20followed%20the%20laid%20down%20procedures.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20had%20even%20gone%20beyond%20all%20the%20legal%20provisions%20available%20by%20trying%20to%20bring%20a%20mutual%20understanding%20among%20all%20the%20contesting%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20statement%20has%20been%20furnished%20to%20the%20Lokayukta%20%E2%80%93%20you%20may%20see%20it%20for%20yourself.%20The%20complainant%20party%20makes%20claims%20that%20several%20court%20cases%20are%20still%20pending.%20However%2C%20if%20none%20of%20them%20relates%20to%20the%20award%20matter%2C%20specifically%20forbidding%20the%20District%20Collector%20from%20paying%20the%20compensation%2C%20how%20can%20any%20work%20make%20any%20progress%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20because%20someone%20filed%20a%20case%20today%2C%20and%20even%20without%20the%20court%20order%2C%20does%20it%20mean%20the%20DC%20has%20to%20stop%20working%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20unfavourable%20judgment%3F%20Absolutely%20not.%20Do%20you%20think%20any%20land%20acquisition%20would%20have%20happened%20if%20we%20had%20followed%20that%20route%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20should%20at%20least%20have%20the%20confidence%20in%20the%20system%20when%20they%20approach%20for%20justice%2C%20rather%20than%20ridiculing%20it%20when%20the%20judgment%20is%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20maintain%20that%20you%20acted%20as%20per%20court%20orders.%20Then%20why%20did%20the%20Lokayukta%20overlook%20your%20statement%20and%20rule%20in%20the%20preliminary%20inquiry%20as%20it%20did%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Having%20furnished%20all%20my%20statements%2C%20and%20also%20all%20relevant%20annexures%2C%20I%20was%20hoping%20that%20the%20matter%20would%20be%20concluded%20here%20and%20then.%20However%2C%20this%20being%20only%20the%20preliminary%20report%2C%20I%20believe%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%20would%20be%20able%20to%20conclude%20the%20matter%20as%20per%20all%20existing%20documents%20in%20record.%20I%20also%20have%20been%20informed%20that%20Lokayukta%20have%20taken%20all%20files%20available%20in%20the%20office%20of%20DC%20office%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20they%20would%20understand%20the%20entire%20proceeding%20of%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process%20and%20the%20intricacies%20that%20follows%20and%20how%20much%20each%20of%20us%20as%20DC%20does%20to%20bring%20all%20land%20acquisition%20matter%20to%20close%20and%20bring%20forth%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Lokayukta%20is%20an%20oversight%20body%2C%20meant%20to%20look%20at%20corruption.%20It%20faults%20your%20actions%20on%20procedure.%20What%20do%20you%20propose%20to%20do%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20I%20would%20not%20like%20to%20question%20the%20jurisdictions%20and%20the%20methods%20adopted%20by%20Lokayukta%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20preliminary%20report%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20Lokayukta%20is%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegation%20of%20corruption%20rather%20than%20the%20procedures%20of%20land%20acquisition%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%20would%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20am%20yet%20to%20receive%20any%20official%20intimation%20from%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%2C%20so%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20comment%20much%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20furnishing%20these%20facts%20based%20on%20some%20reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-lokayukta-ias-officer%5C%22%3Ecarried%20by%20%3Cem%3ET%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ehe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20August%206%2C%202023.%20As%20stated%20in%20the%20above%20few%20court%20cases%20mentioned%2C%20all%20acts%20done%20by%20me%20in%20the%20official%20capacity%20as%20District%20Collector%20of%20Tamenglong%20have%20been%20justified%20by%20the%20competent%20court.%20While%20I%20still%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%20that%20such%20malicious%20complaints%20would%20be%20outrightly%20rejected%20because%20if%20all%20such%20fictitious%20complaints%20are%20to%20be%20entertained%2C%20we%20would%20not%20see%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20railways%20as%20we%20have%20witnessed%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20competent%20and%20honest%20officer%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20take%20up%20any%20decision%20in%20the%20future%20if%20such%20complaints%20are%20continued%20to%20be%20entertained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20legal%20battle%2C%20there%20can%20only%20be%20one%20party%20that%20emerges%20victorious.%20If%20the%20aggrieved%20party%20continues%20to%20endlessly%20fight%20in%20all%20available%20forums%2C%20they%20are%20simply%20wasting%20time%2C%20energy%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20zeal%20of%20the%20officer%20to%20serve%20the%20nation.%20In%20this%20matter%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Marangjing%20have%20taken%20up%20protests%20against%20me%20in%20all%20possible%20forums%2C%20carried%20out%20strikes%2C%20and%20even%20burnt%20my%20effigies.%20Having%20gone%20through%20all%20these%2C%20I%20would%20say%20my%20morale%20is%20definitely%20down%20but%20I%20would%20have%20to%20keep%20fighting%20as%20I%20believe%20my%20commitment%20towards%20the%20development%20of%20the%20nation%20is%20bigger%20than%20their%20hatred%20and%20jealousy%20against%20me.%20In%20all%20of%20these%2C%20I%20hope%20that%20all%20the%20people%20in%20the%20system%2C%20including%20my%20well-wishers%20and%20the%20media%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20stand%20for%20the%20truth%20and%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20me%20this%20was%20already%20a%20concluded%20matter.%20The%20Maringjing%20village%20took%20up%20this%20matter%20again%20only%20after%20almost%20a%20gap%20of%20four%20years%2C%20knowing%20fully%20well%20that%20I%20am%20no%20longer%20in%20Manipur%2C%20leaving%20me%20defenceless%2C%20without%20being%20physically%20present.%20Such%20a%20calculated%20move%20by%20the%20Maringjing%20village%20was%20never%20expected%20as%20I%20thought%20we%20parted%20ways%20on%20good%20terms.%20It%20looks%20like%20this%20village%20is%20now%20committed%20to%20destroying%20my%20career%20no%20matter%20what.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20many%20more%20cases%20they%20will%20put%20up.%20But%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20a%20legal%20battle%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20of%20winning%20them%20all%2C%20because%20I%20had%20done%20it%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20the%20fruit%20of%20such%20hard%20work%20by%20all%20of%20us%2C%20including%20many%20officers%20%5Bwho%20worked%5D%20before%20and%20after%20me%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20railways%20coming%20to%20Manipur%20especially%2C%20in%20this%20time%20of%20crisis%20where%20essential%20commodities%20are%20carried%20on%20trains%20in%20bulk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13122920%2Fimage-1217.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22874%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13122920%2Fimage-1217.png%20705w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13122920%2Fimage-1217-300x227.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22662%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20goods%20train%20reached%20Khongshang%20Station%20on%20July%2024%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20only%20wish%20that%20one%20day%2C%20the%20Marangjing%20villagers%20see%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20development%20as%20theirs%20and%20that%20along%20with%20that%2C%20they%20also%20see%20the%20career%20advancement%20of%20officers%2C%20including%20me%2C%20as%20their%20own%20success%20