ulated%20that%20the%20gangs%20are%20using%20jetpacks%20to%20reach%20more%20unattainable%20spots%20in%20the%20dense%20jungles%20near%20the%20Nanay%20River%20to%20mine%20for%20more%20gold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20be%20using%20state-of-the-art%20technology%2C%20such%20as%20thrusters%20that%20allow%20people%20to%20fly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Carlos%20Castro%20Quintanilla%2C%20the%20Peruvian%20government's%20prosecutor%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20told%20Radio%20Programas%20del%20Peru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20that%20the%20jetpacks%20were%20first%20used%20by%20these%20illegal%20mining%20cartels%20to%20explore%20prospects%20for%20gold%20deeper%20in%20the%20forest%20surrounding%20the%20Nanay%20River%20in%20Peru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Cem%3E%20New%20York%20Post%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Alto%20Nanay%20is%20rich%20in%20gold%2C%20and%20metal%20is%20deposited%20in%20the%20riverbeds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alien%20debate%20started%20on%20July%2011%20when%20locals%20started%20complaining%20of%20attacks%20by%20a%207-foot-tall%20creature%20that%20was%20clothed%20in%20dark-coloured%20hoods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20eye%20witness%20who%20is%20a%20school%20teacher%20claimed%20that%20the%20strange%20alien-like%20creature%20was%20flying%20from%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2015-year-old%20reportedly%20was%20cut%20on%20the%20neck%20in%20one%20of%20the%20attacks%20and%20required%20treatment%20at%20a%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ikitu%20community%20has%20asked%20the%20military%20to%20intervene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691922420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ftmsrt438_alien-unsplash_625x300_13_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fperus-7-foot-tall-aliens-turn-out-to-be-illegal-gold-miners-say-officials-4294453%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20locals%20even%20compared%20the%20attackers%20to%20'green%20goblins'%20and%20many%