gency%20on%20Corruption%20Prevention%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fzelensky-fires-heads-ukraines-military-call-centers-1819140%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENewsweek%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commissars%2C%20Zelenskyy's%20Telegram%20message%20added%2C%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20%26quot%3Bsoldiers%20who%20have%20been%20to%20the%20front%20or%20who%20cannot%20be%20in%20the%20trenches%20because%20they%20have%20lost%20their%20health%2C%20lost%20their%20limbs%2C%20but%20have%20retained%20their%20dignity%20and%20have%20no%20cynicism%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20be%20entrusted%20with%20this%20recruitment%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorruption%20scandals%20have%20plagued%20Ukraine%20over%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20saying%20in%202015%20that%20it%20was%20eating%20the%20country%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fjoe-biden-corruption-eating-ukraine-like-a-cancer%2F%5C%22%3Elike%20a%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcorruption-in-ukraine-zelenskyy-is-responsible-says-national-survey-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691921848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d6315c005c4a00183deeee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcorruption-in-ukraine-zelenskyy-is-responsible-says-national-survey-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20three-quarters%20of%C2%A0Ukrainians%20said%20they%20believed%20that%20Zelenskyy%20was%20responsible%20for%20corruption%20in%20the%20military%20and%20government%20administrations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nrennolds%40insider.com%20(Nathan%20Rennolds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcorruption-in-ukraine-zelenskyy-is-responsible-s