at%20crucial%20balance%20between%20remote%20flexibility%20and%20in-person%20connection%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20noted%20that%20the%20company%20believes%20both%20hybrid%20work%20and%20flexibility%20aren't%20going%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTime%20and%20time%20again%2C%20our%20external%20data%20has%20shown%20us%20that%20people%20want%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%3A%20flexible%20work%20and%20connection%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BOur%20first%20annual%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dc9b8ddacb51536422ec35d9254a693d1d4a202510f329e9f920b22c5d452f404%26postID%3D64cd5b54cfd91a08ec463358%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.microsoft.com%252Fen-us%252Fworklab%252Fwork-trend-index%252Fhybrid-work-is-just-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWork%20Trend%20Index%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20external%20survey%20of%20thousands%20of%20workers%20worldwide%2C%20uncovered%20what%20we%20call%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D9b7fb242aef2dd98484bff1e43a4d46c0cb1158a00583ea96036d5c3de504b66%26postID%3D64cd5b54cfd91a08ec463358%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.microsoft.com%252Fen-us%252Fworklab%252Fpodcast%252Fhybrid-work-paradox%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20paradox%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Over%2070%25%20of%20workers%20told%20us%20they%20wanted%20flexible%20work%20to%20stay%2C%20while%20over%2065%25%20said%20were%20craving%20more%20in-person%20time%20with%20their%20teams.%20We've%20seen%20this%20trend%20persist%20in%20both%20our%20external%20research%20and%20in%20our%20internal%20employee%20surveys%20at%20Microsoft.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20had%20a%20hybrid-work%20policy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2022%2F03%2F02%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-office-return-april-4%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Efor%20over%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Ryan%20Lamont%2C%20a%20Google%20spokesperson.%20The%20policy%20has%20become%20more%20integrated%20in%20the%20past%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20hybrid%20approach%20is%20designed%20to%20incorporate%20the%20best%20of%20being%20together%20in%20person%20with%20the%20benefits%20of%20working%20from%20home%20for%20part%20of%20the%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamont%20told%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BNow%20that%20we're%20more%20than%20a%20year%20into%20this%20way%20of%20working%2C%20we're%20formally%20integrating%20this%20approach%20into%20all%20of%20our%20workplace%20policies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fgoogle-gets-stricter-about-employees-time-in-office-9a20f2e%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20June%20that%20office%20attendance%20for%20Google%20workers%20may%20be%20considered%20in%20reviews%20and%20that%20people%20who%20are%20often%20absent%20from%20the%20office%20will%20get%20reminders.%20Lamont%20told%20Insider%20that%20office-badge%20data%20won't%20be%20shared%20with%20managers%20for%20measuring%20employee%20performance%20but%20is%20being%20used%20to%20gauge%20things%20like%20employees%20being%20absent%20from%20the%20office%20for%20multiple%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20heard%20from%20Googlers%20that%20those%20who%20spend%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%20in%20the%20office%20feel%20more%20connected%20to%20other%20Googlers%2C%20and%20that%20this%20effect%20is%20magnified%20when%20teammates%20work%20from%20the%20same%20location%2C%26quot%3B%20Fiona%20Cicconi%2C%20Google's%20chief%20people%20officer%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20company%20email%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-monitors-attendance-to-get-workers-back-to-office-2023-6%5C%22%3Eprevious%20reporting%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Alphabet%20Workers%20Union%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAlphabetWorkers%2Fstatus%2F1666839673690546176%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20in%20June%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3BGoogle%20announced%20the%20company%20would%20begin%20the%20enforcement%20of%20their%20RTO%20policy.%26quot%3B%20Alphabet%20is%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20teams%20are%20distributed%2C%20and%20for%20some%20of%20us%20there%20may%20not%20be%20anyone%20to%20collaborate%20with%20in%20our%20physical%20office%20locations%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Schmidt%2C%20a%20software%20engineer%20and%20Alphabet%20Workers%20Union-CWA%20member%2C%20said%20in%20the%20statement%20that%20was%20part%20of%20the%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BCurrently%2C%20New%20York%20City%20workers%20do%20not%20even%20have%20enough%20desks%20and%20conference%20rooms%20for%20workers%20to%20use%20comfortably.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20one%20size%20fits%20all%20policy%20does%20not%20address%20these%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20continued.%20%26quot%3BWe%20deserve%20a%20voice%20in%20shaping%20the%20policies%20that%20impact%20our%20lives%20to%20establish%20clear%2C%20transparent%20and%20fair%20working%20conditions%20for%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIBM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20IBM%2C%20most%20of%20our%20employees%20are%20co-located%20near%20an%20IBM%20office%20or%20client%2C%20and%20routinely%20collaborate%20and%20co-create%20in%20face-to-face%20environments%2C%26quot%3B%20Nickle%20LaMoreaux%2C%20the%20senior%20vice%20president%20and%20chief%20human%20resources%20officer%20at%20IBM%2C%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-for-job-seekers-looking-for-flexible-work-2022-10%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIBM%20has%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bphased%20approach%20in%20returning%20IBM%20employees%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.ibm.com%2Findex.php%3Fs%3D34178%26item%3D32071%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIBM's%20newsroom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20almost%20all%20of%20IBM%20was%20working%20remotely%20in%20March%202020%2C%20managers%20are%20now%20leading%20the%20workplace%20decisions%20for%20their%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIBM's%20approach%20before%20the%20pandemic%20and%20currently%20is%20focused%20on%20intentional%20flexibility%20with%20collaboration%20decided%20by%20team-%20and%20job-based%20norms%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20IBM%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20allows%20teams%20to%20decide%20flexible%20hours%20that%20are%20best%20for%20people%20to%20work%2C%20when%20they%20need%20to%20come%20together%20in%20face-to-face%20environments%20and%20what%20they%20are%20working%20on.%20Managers%20design%20what%20works%20for%20their%20teams%20so%20that%20their%20time%20at%20the%20office%20is%20used%20to%20collaborate%20and%20co-create.%20This%20flexibility%20helps%20serve%20both%20the%20individual%20and%20how%20work%20gets%20done%20as%20a%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20the%20tech%20sector%2C%20companies%20are%20also%20prioritizing%20hybrid%20work.%20That%20includes%20consulting%20firm%20EY.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrank%20Giampietro%2C%20the%20Americas%20chief%20well-being%20officer%20for%20EY%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20EY%20US%20%26quot%3Bhad%20worked%20with%20a%20design%20council%20of%20about%20a%20hundred%20people%20across%20parts%20of%20our%20business%20to%20sort%20of%20look%20at%20the%20work%20that%20they%20did%20and%20then%20to%20really%20try%20to%20map%20out%20what%20those%20interactions%20would%20look%20like%20for%20different%20types%20of%20work%20that%20we%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20that%2C%20EY%20believed%20people%20in%20most%20positions%20would%20spend%2040%25%20to%2060%25%20working%20in%20person%20with%20others.%20That%20in-person%20time%2C%20Giampietro%20said%2C%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bfor%20what%20we%20call%20moments%20that%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20relationships%20and%20connectedness%2C%20on-the-job%20learning%2C%20coaching%2C%20feedback%2C%20and%20then%20really%20kind%20of%20ideation%20and%20complex%20collaboration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Giampietro%20noted%20the%20challenge%20of%20hybrid%20work%20for%20meeting%20with%20clients%2C%20as%20some%20of%20%26quot%3Bthose%20clients%20may%20not%20be%20in%20as%20frequently%20or%20may%20not%20want%20us%20in%20as%20frequently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiampietro%20said%20that%20the%20company's%20thinking%20was%20initially%20hypothesis-driven%3B%20now%2C%20based%20on%20internal%20data%20EY%20has%20gathered%20and%20other%20research%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20believe%20hybrid%20is%20the%20right%20approach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20are%20working%20together%20two%20to%20three%20days%20a%20week%20in%20person%2C%20they're%20having%20higher%20flexibility%20and%20higher%20well-being%20scores%20than%20those%20people%20who%20are%20predominantly%20working%20on%20site%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Giampietro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKaty%20George%2C%20a%20senior%20partner%20and%20the%20chief%20people%20officer%20at%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bfor%20the%20most%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20consulting%20company%20tries%20%26quot%3Bto%20leave%20it%20to%20our%20individual%20teams%20to%20decide%20what%20works%20best%20for%20them%26quot%3B%20and%20their%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20urge%20people%20to%20take%20full%20advantage%20of%20the%20benefits%20that%20are%20very%20clear%20of%20colocating%20as%20well%20as%20the%20benefits%20of%20having%20the%20flexibility%20of%20virtual%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20really%20are%20embracing%20a%20hybrid%20mindset.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20noted%20that%20McKinsey's%20analytics%20team%20found%20that%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3Bsweet%20spot%20of%20being%20close%20to%2050%25%20colocated%26quot%3B%20which%2C%20for%20McKinsey%20staff%2C%20means%20located%20at%20one%20of%20their%20offices%20or%20with%20a%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20get%20to%20that%2050%25%20colocation%2C%20we%20see%20client%20feedback%20and%20satisfaction%20going%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20the%20teams%20having%20more%20fun%20and%20feeling%20more%20connected.%20We%20also%20see%20retention%20rates%20going%20up%2C%20and%20we%20see%20markers%20that%20people%20are%20getting%20better%20apprenticeships%20and%20getting%20more%20opportunities%20to%20learn%20and%20grow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20George%20said%2C%20after%20the%2050%25%20colocation%20mark%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20don't%20see%20a%20linear%20continued%20improvement%20on%20those%20outcomes%20by%20being%20in%20person%20more%20and%20more%20and%20more.%26quot%3B%20Given%20that%2C%20George%20said%20workers%20are%20encouraged%20to%20%26quot%3Breally%20take%20advantage%20of%20virtual%20work%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20have%20projects%20that%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20done%20with%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDid%20you%20return%20to%20the%20office%20a%20few%20days%20a%20week%20or%20every%20day%20after%20working%20from%20home%20during%20the%20pandemic%3F%20Are%20you%20a%20hybrid%20worker%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emhoff%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20story%20and%20how%20you%20feel%20about%20your%20company's%20current%20remote%2C%20hybrid%2C%20or%20in-person%20work%20policy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-microsoft-ib