hat%20was%20in%20India%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%20from%20August%2010%20to%2012%2C%20primarily%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20anti-corruption%20ministerial%20meeting%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20he%20held%20talks%20with%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20Security%20Minister%20was%20replying%20to%20a%20question%20on%20India's%20persistent%20demand%20for%20extradition%20of%20a%20number%20of%20economic%20offenders%20including%20Vijay%20Mallya%20and%20Nirav%20Modi%2C%20who%20are%20living%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirav%20Modi%2C%20the%20fugitive%20diamond%20merchant%2C%20is%20wanted%20in%20India%20to%20stand%20trial%20on%20fraud%20and%20money%20laundering%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2052-year-old%20businessman%20last%20year%20lost%20his%20legal%20battle%20in%20the%20highest%20UK%20court%20against%20being%20extradited%20to%20India%20in%20the%20estimated%20USD%202%20billion%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20loan%20scam%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20case%20is%20now%20said%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bstatute%20barred%26quot%3B%2C%20indicating%20further%20pending%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Mallya%2C%20who%20fled%20to%20the%20UK%20in%20March%202016%2C%20is%20wanted%20in%20India%20over%20a%20default%20of%20Rs%209%2C000%20crore%20that%20was%20loaned%20to%20Kingfisher%20Airlines%20by%20several%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20talks%20with%20NSA%20Doval%2C%20the%20British%20Security%20Minister%20declined%20to%20share%20the%20details%20but%20noted%20that%20the%20broad%20bilateral%20cooperation%20is%20focused%20on%20security%20of%20the%20two%20nations%20and%20the%20prosperity%20of%20the%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20talking%20about%20the%20security%20of%20our%20two%20nations%20and%20the%20prosperity%20of%20our%20citizens%2C%20their%20ability%20to%20conduct%20their%20business%20at%20home%2