20everything%20possible%20to%20protect%20the%20Kim%20dynasty's%20portraits%20as%20the%20country%20braces%20for%20heavy%20rains%20and%20high%20gusts%20from%20typhoon%20Khanun%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Feast-asia%2Fnorth-korea-kim-jong-un-portrait-storm-khanun-general-b2391490.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Rodong%20Sinmun%2C%20the%20official%20newspaper%20of%20the%20ruling%20Korean%20Workers'%20Party%2C%20stated%20that%20people's%20%26quot%3Bforemost%20focus%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bensuring%20the%20safety%26quot%3B%20of%20propaganda%20images%20of%20North%20Korea's%20current%20leader%2C%20Kim%20Jong-un%2C%20his%20father%2C%20Kim%20Jong-il%2C%20and%20his%20grandfather%2C%20Kim%20Il-Sung.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state-run%20newspaper%20also%20urged%20North%20Koreans%20to%20safeguard%20sculptures%2C%20monuments%2C%20mosaics%2C%20and%20paintings%20of%20the%20Kim%20dynasty%2C%20which%20has%20ruled%20the%20country%20since%20it%20was%20founded%20in%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Pyongyang%20is%20extremely%20sensitive%20to%20the%20situation%20as%20portraits%20of%20the%20dynasty%20are%20found%20in%20several%20homes%20and%20offices.%20As%20per%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3Bcitizens%20face%20possible%20prosecution%20if%20failed%20to%20safeguard%20the%20portraits%20during%20a%20disaster%2C%20such%20as%20fire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20professor%20at%20Kookmin%20University%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ENK%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20not%20forget%20that%20North%20Korea%20among%20other%20things%20is%20a%20theocratic%20state.%20These%20statues%20and%20portraits%20are%20not%20just%20symbols%20but%20are%20sacred%20religious%20symbols%20-%20essentially%20icons.%20Every%20religion%20since%20times%20immemorial%20expects%20its%20faithful%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20die%20-%20or%20at%20least%20suffer%20-%20in%20order%20to%20save%20sacred%20icons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20hundreds%20of%20South%20Koreans%20were%20evacuated%20from%20coastal%20areas%20on%20Thursday%20as%20the%20storm%20battered%20the%20country's%20southern%20provinces.%20Cumulative%20rainfall%20in%20certain%20regions%20has%20exceeded%20400mm%2C%20with%20maximum%20wind%20gusts%20of%20126%20km%20per%20hour%2C%20flooding%20villages%2C%20schools%20and%20roadways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20interior%20ministry%2C%20about%2016%2C000%20people%20were%20evacuated%2C%20but%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20them%20had%20returned%20to%20their%20homes%20as%20of%206%20am%20on%20Friday.%20Additionally%2C%20around%20350%20flights%20and%20450%20rail%20lines%20were%20disrupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691920080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Ftnub6d7_kim-jong-un-afp_625x300_02_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforemost-focus-north-koreans-told-to-protect-kim-jong-un-portraits-as-typhoon-approaches-4294391%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20capital%20city%20of%20Pyongyang%20is%20extremely%20sensitive%20to%20the%20situation%20as%20portraits%20of%20the%20dynasty%20are%20found%20in%20several%20homes%20and%20offices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforemost-focus-north-koreans-told-to-protect-kim-jong-un-portraits-as-typhoon-approaches-4294391%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforemost-focus-north-koreans-told-to-protect-kim-jong-un-portraits-as-typhoon-approaches-4294391%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fforemost-focus-north-koreans-told-to-protect-kim-jong-un-portraits-as-typhoon-approaches-4294391%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aaradhya's%20video%20from%20school%20goes%20viral!%20Watch%22%2C%22content%22%