3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0had%20received%20funds%20from%20China%20to%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%E2%80%9D%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20was%20published%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENafrat%20ki%20Dukaan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20(shop%20of%20hate)%20has%20Chinese%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esamaan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(goods)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dubey%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20article%20had%20said%20that%20Rs%2038%20crore%20has%20been%20received%20by%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabhir%20Purkayastha%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20owner%2C%20issued%20a%20statement%20denying%20%E2%80%9Cany%20insinuation%20that%20%5B%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%20function%5Bs%5D%20as%20a%20mouth-piece%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20or%20other%20interests%E2%80%9D%20is%20false.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20BJP%20MPs%20soon%20afterwards%20shared%20the%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20piece%20multiple%20times%20to%20attack%20the%20news%20portal%2C%20some%20independent%20journalists%20and%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ftargeted-campaign-newsclick-unwarranted-pci-iwpc%5C%22%3Efour%20media%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%2C%20the%20Indian%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Press%20Corps%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20and%20Press%20Association%20%E2%80%93%20issued%20a%20joint%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20expressing%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20targeted%20campaign%2C%20calling%20that%20the%20insinuation%20that%20it%20is%20a%20China%20mouthpiece%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunwarranted%20and%20condemnable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20this%20year%2C%20Twitter%E2%80%99s%20former%20owner%20Jack%20Dorsey%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fjack-dorsey-rajeev-chandrasekhar-twitter-takedown-india-farmers-protests%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20had%20made%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20requests%E2%80%9D%20to%20Twitter%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20for%20the%20deletion%20of%20content%20by%20journalists%20critical%20of%20official%20policy%20and%20also%20threatened%20to%20shut%20down%20Twitter%20in%20India%20and%20raid%20its%20employees%E2%80%99%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20new%20owner%20Elon%20Musk%20has%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20been%20keen%20to%20follow%20domestic%20rules.%20He%20told%20the%20BBC%20in%20April%20this%20year%20that%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Felon-musk-bbc-interview-india-it-rules%5C%22%3Elikely%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20blocking%20orders%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0issued%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20instead%20of%20facing%20a%20situation%20where%20Twitter%20employees%20could%20be%20sent%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691915262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13135310%2FUntitled-design-6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclicks-twitter-account-suspended-days-after-bjp-mps-chinese-links-allegation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20comes%20within%20days%20of%20a%20BJP%20MP%20citing%20a%20'New%20York%20Times'%20piece%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20news%20site%20is%20a%20China%20mouthpiece.%20Four%20media%20bodies%20have%20called%20this%20insinuation%20%E2%80%9Cunwarranted%20and%20condemnable%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclicks-twitter-account-suspended-days-after-bjp-mps-chinese-links-allegation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'We%20Lived%20There%20for%2030%20Years%20But%20Can't%20Go%20Back%20Now'%3A%20Accounts%20of%20Loss%20From%20a%20Land%20of%20Zero%20FIRs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13133010%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-13-at-12.41.44-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaikul%20(Manipur)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20During%20the%20night%20time%2C%20when%20many%20residents%20of%20Manipur%20stay%20up%20and%20guard%20their%20villages%2C%20this%20reporter%20reached%20the%20small%20down%20of%20Saikul%20in%20the%20hills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20located%2028%20kilometres%20from%20Kangpokpi%20and%2035%20kilometres%20from%20Imphal.%20Its%20population%20is%20around%2070%2C000.%20The%20town%20has%20only%20two%20doctors%20in%20the%20community%20health%20centre.%20Earlier%2C%20they%20had%20four.%20Two%20of%20them%20were%20Meiteis%20and%20had%20to%20leave%20Saikul%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20early%20May.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Near%20the%20mountain%20in%20the%20town%2C%20in%20a%20small%20house%2C%20a%20Kuki%20family%20waits%20for%20justice.%20Thangkholal%20and%20Hemang%20heard%20about%20the%20killing%20of%20their%20mother%20and%20sisters%20while%20they%20were%20in%20Imphal.%20The%20two%20used%20to%20live%20with%20their%2086-year-old%20mother%20Veinem%20Chongloi%20and%20their%20two%20sisters%2C%20Helma%20(50)%20and%20Hekim%20(47)%2C%20in%20Takhellambam%20Leikai%2C%20located%20in%20Imphal%20West.%20Their%20house%20was%20a%20rented%20one%20and%20one%20in%20which%20they%20had%20lived%20for%20almost%2030%20years%20till%20May%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20May%203%2C%20ethnic%20violence%20began%20in%20Manipur%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20arson.%20More%20than%20142%20people%20died%20in%20it%2C%20as%20is%20well%20known%20now.%20Veinem%2C%20along%20with%20her%20two%20daughters%2C%20was%20killed%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20May%204%20by%20a%20mob.%20Locals%20say%20it%20was%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20May%204%2C%20Thangkholal%20and%20Hemang%20ran%20from%20their%20home%20with%20no%20money%20in%20hand%2C%20wearing%20only%20a%20single%20set%20of%20clothes.%20They%20reached%20Saikul%20where%20their%20third%20sister%20and%20only%20surviving%20family%20member%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20brothers%E2%80%99%20father%20had%20worked%20at%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%20Their%20landlord%2C%20a%20Meitei%20community%20member%2C%20had%20not%20been%20charging%20them%20rent%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%20%E2%80%93%20ever%20since%20the%20father%20died.%20The%20family%20discussed%20the%20violence%20with%20their%20landlord%20on%20May%203%20as%20well%20but%20never%20imagined%20that%20their%20lives%20would%20change%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20May%204%2C%20at%2011%20am%2C%20we%20received%20a%20call%20from%20our%20local%20MLA%2C%20who%20is%20Meitei%2C%20telling%20us%20not%20to%20go%20out%20and%20to%20lock%20the%20doors%20from%20inside.%20Later%2C%20Meira%20Paibis%20%5Bwoman%20vigilantes%20belonging%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%5D%20came%20to%20our%20house%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20open%20our%20door.%20We%20told%20them%20about%20the%20situation%20and%20the%20MLA%E2%80%99s%20call.%20They%20asked%20us%20to%20call%20the%20MLA%20again.%20But%20the%20MLA%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pick%20up%20the%20call%2C%20and%20then%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20summoned%20the%20mob%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thangkholal%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVeinem%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20were%20bad%2C%20so%20the%20sisters%20advised%20the%20brothers%20to%20run%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20would%20hold%20fort%20with%20their%20mother.%20%E2%80%9COur%20sisters%20thought%20the%20mob%20would%20not%20attack%20them%20as%20they%20were%20all%20women.%20As%20we%20ran%2C%20we%20heard%20our%20sisters%E2%80%99%20screams%20and%20then%20the%20declaration%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20have%20killed%20all%20three%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hemand%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhotos%20of%20the%20two%20sisters%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20showed%20that%20their%20faces%20could%20have%20been%20maimed%20with%20sharp%20weapons.%20The%20brothers%20said%20they%20do%20not%20know%20what%20has%20happened%20to%20their%20mother.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThangkholal%20and%20Hemang%20first%20ran%20from%20the%20area%20to%20the%20house%20of%20their%20Meitei%20friend%2C%20who%20allowed%20them%20to%20stay%20for%20some%20time.%20But%20the%20mob%20found%20them%20there%20too%2C%20they%20said.%20They%20sought%20shelter%20in%20another%20Meitei%20friend%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20only%20to%20be%20followed%20there%20by%20the%20mob%20again.%20The%20third%20location%20they%20reached%20was%20Lamphel%20Baptist%20Church%2C%20but%20after%20spending%20some%20time%20there%2C%20they%20heard%20that%20churches%20were%20also%20being%20burnt%2C%20so%20they%20left%20the%20place%20and%20took%20shelter%20at%20yet%20another%20Meitei%20friend%E2%80%99s%20house.%20Then%2C%20the%20Imphal%20West%20superintendent%20of%20police%20came%20to%20their%20rescue%20and%20took%20them%20to%20the%20Manipur%20Rifles%20Battalion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20May%205%2C%20I%20called%20my%20landlord%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20check%20if%20my%20mother%20and%20sisters%20are%20still%20alive.%20The%20landlord%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%98Do%20you%20know%20that%20a%20Meitei%20lady%20was%20killed%20in%20Churachandpur%3F%E2%80%99%20What%20could%20we%20say%20to%20him%20after%20that%3F%E2%80%9D%20Hemang%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20brothers%20spent%20seven%20days%20at%20the%20Manipur%20Rifles%20camp%2C%20and%20then%2C%20soldiers%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20dropped%20them%20off%20at%20Kangpokpi%2C%20from%20where%20they%20reached%20Saikul.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13133329%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-1.31.45.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13133329%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-1.31.45.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13133329%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-1.31.45-300x200.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13133329%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-1.31.45-1024x684.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667871%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22801%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMen%20rest%20at%20Saikul.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArea%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20area%20where%20the%20family%20used%20to%20live%20was%20a%20Meitei-dominated%20area%2C%20and%20they%20were%20the%20lone%20Kuki%20family%20living%20there%20for%20years.%20Yumnam%20Joykumar%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur%20and%20who%20also%20retired%20as%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20director%20general%20of%20police%2C%20lives%20in%20the%20same%20area%20where%20the%20crime%20happened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20brothers%20filed%20an%20FIR%20on%20May%2017%2C%202023%2C%20at%209%20am%2C%20just%20after%20reaching%20Saikul.%20It%20was%20a%20zero%20FIR%2C%20filed%20at%20Saikul.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CVeenem%20Chongloi%2C%20Helam%20Chongloi%2C%20and%20Hekim%20Chongloi%20were%20murdered%20using%20sharp%20objects%20and%20firearms.%20The%20case%20was%20filed%20under%20302%2F34%20IPC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20complaint%20filed%20by%20Hemang%2C%20he%20named%20%E2%80%9Cunknown%20miscreants%E2%80%9D%20who%20are%20suspected%20to%20belong%20Meitei%20youth%20organisations%20like%20the%20%E2%80%9CMeetei%20Leepun%2C%20Kangleipak%20Kanba%20Lup%20(KKL)%2C%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20World%20Meitei%20Council%20(WMC)%2C%20and%20Schedule%20Tribe%20Demand%20Committee%20(STDC).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20said%20they%20numbered%20between%20100%20and%20200.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20three%20murders%2C%20the%20brothers%E2%80%99%20complaint%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20looted%20all%20the%20household%20properties%2C%20including%20jewellery%2C%20furniture%2C%20electronic%20items%2C%20ornaments%2C%20utensils%2C%20important%20documents%2C%20clothes%2C%20food%2C%20and%20grains%20worth%20about%20Rs.%2010-15%20lakhs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20visited%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Uripok%20Takhellambam%20Leikai%2C%20Imphal%2C%20but%20women%20who%20identified%20themselves%20as%20Meira%20Paibis%20in%20the%20area%20did%20not%20let%20this%20reporter%20ask%20neighbours%20about%20the%20family.%20The%20family%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20now%20being%20handled%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%20The%20bodies%20of%20the%20three%20women%20are%20at%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20RIIMS%20Hospital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20total%20of%20217%20FIRs%20were%20registered%20at%20the%20Saikul%20police%20station.%20All%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20police%20stations%20in%20Imphal.%20Goupu%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Students%20Organisation%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20already%20know%20that%20Manipur%20government%20itself%20is%20the%20main%20culprit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoupu%20cited%20how%20the%20DGP%20P.%20Doungel%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%20and%20was%20transferred%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20(Home)%20in%20June%2C%20and%20replaced%20by%20Rajiv%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20FIR%20at%20Saikul%20notes%20how%20two%20Kuki%20men%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ELetgunchon%20Touthang%20(18)%20and%20Thangmilen%20Vaiphei%20(32)%2C%20who%20used%20to%20work%20in%20a%20furniture%20store%20in%20Imphal%20East%2C%20were%20brutally%20killed%20with%20firearms%20and%20other%20deadly%20weapons%20on%20the%20night%20of%20May%204.%20The%20FIR%20notes%20that%20members%20of%20the%20same%20organisations%20are%20accused%20in%20this%20case%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20with%20an%20eyewitness%20of%20the%20murder%2C%20Shiv%20Prasad%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20who%20captured%20the%20murder%20of%20the%20two%20on%20camera.%20%E2%80%9COn%20that%20day%2C%20people%20were%20checking%20our%20ID%20cards.%20We%20were%20eight%20people%2C%20three%20Kuki%2C%20and%20two%20of%20us%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20They%20killed%20all%20three%20upon%20getting%20to%20know%20they%20were%20Kuki%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691914082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13133010%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-13-at-12.41.44-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-ground-report-kuki-meitei-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kuki%20brothers%20Thangkholal%20and%20Hemang's%20Meitei%20landlord%20had%20stopped%20charging%20them%20rent%20when%20he%20learnt%20their%20father%20had%20died.%20But%20that%20didn't%20stop%20an%20allegedly%20Meitei%20mob%20from%20attacking%20them%20and%20killing%20three%20members%20of%20their%20family%20on%20May%204.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-ground-report-kuki-meitei-violence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FIRs%20against%20Priyanka%2C%20Nath%20over%20'50%25%20commission'%20barb%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691913745000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http