tions%20made%20by%20Hindenburg%20Research%20against%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeloitte%2C%20therefore%2C%20said%20that%20it%20cannot%20comment%20if%20the%20company%20was%20fully%20compliant%20with%20local%20laws%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAPSEZ%20said%20Deloitte%20had%20resigned%20because%20it%20was%20not%20given%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwider%20audit%20role%E2%80%9D%20covering%20other%20listed%20Adani%20portfolio%20companies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-resigns-as-the-statutory-auditors-of-adani-ports-and-special-economic-zone%2Fcid%2F1958682%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20claimed%20that%20Deloitte%20had%20indicated%20its%20position%20at%20a%20recent%20meeting%20with%20the%20APSEZ%20management%20and%20its%20audit%20committee%2C%20which%20comprises%20four%20independent%20directors.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20no%20other%20reasons%20other%20than%20(that)%20mentioned%20in%20the%20resignation%20letter%20received%20from%20the%20statutory%20auditors%20dated%20August%2012.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resignation%20letter%20from%20Deloitte%2C%20which%20was%20appended%20to%20the%20regulatory%20filing%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20tendering%20our%20resignation%20%E2%80%A6with%20immediate%20effect%20because%20we%20are%20not%20statutory%20auditors%20of%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20other%20Adani%20group%20companies%E2%80%A6including%20an%20Adani%20group%20company%20(and%20its%20subsidiaries)%20after%20our%20completion%20of%20our%20term%20of%20five%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20which%20Adani%20group%20company%20Deloitte%20was%20referring%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Ports%20said%20in%20a%20regulatory%20filing%20that%20Deloitte%20had%20been%20its%20statutory%20auditor%20since%20May%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202022%2C%20the%20company%20reappointed%20Deloitte%20as%20its%20statutory%20auditor%20for%20another%20term%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691912001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16195900%2Fadani-pti.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-resigns-as-the-statutory-auditors-of-adani-ports-and-special-economic-zone%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20May%2C%20the%20audit%20firm%20had%20flagged%20some%20transactions%20by%20Adani%20Group%2C%20citing%20allegations%20from%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20that%20wiped%20off%20half%20of%20the%20market%20value%20of%20the%20ports-to-power%20conglomerate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-resigns-as-the-statutory-auditors-of-adani-ports-and-special-economic-zone%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Barbie%20bombed%20in%20South%20Korea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691911800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fthumb%2Fmsid-102652258%2Cwidth-1070%2Cheight-580%2Cimgsize-45680%2Cresizemode-75%2Coverlay-toi_sw%2Cpt-32%2Cy_pad-40%2Fphoto.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-why-barbie-bombed-at-the-south-korean-box-office-find-out%2Farticleshow%2F102652258.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102652258.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20West%20has%20welcomed%20everything%20South%20Korean%2C%20including%20their%20popular%20web%20series%2C%20movies%2C%20and%20K-pop%2C%20but%20the%20South%20Koreans%20haven't%20reciprocated%20that%20with%20Greta%20Gerwig's%20Barbie.%20Since%20its%20debut%20more%20than%20three%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20otherwise%20extreme