thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F12150823%2FIMG_6738.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20long%20last%2C%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20moved%20against%20the%20incumbent%20government%20by%20the%20opposition.%20Given%20the%20brute%20majority%20the%20present%20government%20enjoys%20in%20parliament%2C%20no%20one%20expected%20it%20to%20go%20through.%20But%20it%20was%20what%20the%20writer%20Nadine%20Gordimer%20once%20called%2C%20an%20essential%20gesture%E2%80%9Dof%20a%20group%20acting%20as%20advocates%20of%20the%20national%20interest.%20The%20short%20opening%20speech%20by%20a%20young%20parliamentarian%20from%20the%20area%2C%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20underscored%20the%20urgency%20of%20restoring%20peace%20in%20Manipur%2C%20recounting%20the%20grim%20and%20brutal%20series%20of%20events%20that%20have%20been%20taking%20place%20there.%20It%20was%20a%20moving%20speech%20delivered%20without%20histrionics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20minister%20speaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20his%20party%20and%20ministry%2C%20later%20spoke%20for%20almost%20two%20hours.%20His%20words%20underscored%20the%20strength%20and%20superiority%20of%20the%20government%20over%20the%20previous%20Congress%20governments%E2%80%99%20divisive%20policies%2C%20which%20had%20led%20to%20the%20current%20mess.%20%E2%80%98We%20are%20handling%20it%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20message%2C%20and%20soon%20there%20will%20be%20peace.%20No%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20said.%20The%20speech%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20sharp%20rejoinder%20the%20next%20day.%20He%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20movers%20of%20the%20motion%20as%20expected%2C%20bristling%20with%20sarcasm%20and%20contempt%20for%20the%20new%20united%20opposition%20and%20its%20new%20name%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20a%20wonderful%20ear%20for%20catching%20and%20reproducing%20various%20nuances%20of%20Hindi.%20As%20always%20he%20was%20many-voiced%2C%20frequently%20inserting%20local%20words%20or%20religious%20references%20to%20underscore%20his%20own%20deep%20and%20personal%20%E2%80%98connection%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20peoples%E2%80%99%20mind.%20He%20largely%20skirted%20around%20the%20issue%20of%20Manipur%2C%20referring%20to%20it%20towards%20the%20end%20as%20a%20matter%20where%20the%20nation%20stood%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20between%20the%20two%20stalwarts%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20spoke%20for%20a%20little%20over%2030%20minutes.%20The%20government-owned%20TV%20showed%20him%20for%20only%20a%20few%20of%20those%20focusing%20mostly%20on%20the%20impassive%20face%20of%20the%20Chair.%20But%20his%20message%20was%20straight%20and%20simple%20and%20was%20heard%20and%20watched%20by%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20feels%20strange%20to%20return%20from%20such%20oratorial%20performance%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s.%20Of%20course%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20Hindi%20and%20the%20manner%20of%20speaking%20have%20improved%20vastly%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20but%20it%20is%20still%20nowhere%20close%20to%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Even%20so%20he%20has%20an%20advantage.%20He%20can%20put%20his%20natural%20amiability%20to%20good%20use%20for%20striking%20a%20dialogue%20with%20the%20common%20Indians%20he%20met%20during%20his%20recent%20%3Cem%3Epadyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20more%20recently%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20Manipur.%20It%20was%20the%20pain%2C%20the%20hopes%20and%20the%20longings%20of%20the%20peoples%20of%20India%2C%20in%20particular%20Manipur%2C%20that%20he%20had%20gathered%20that%20gave%20a%20certain%20poignancy%20to%20his%20slightly%20different%20and%20unstructured%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20Modi%20and%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20chaste%20Sanskritised%20Hindi%2C%20Gandhi%20speaks%20a%20hybridized%20Hindi%20most%20young%20Indians%20speak%20today.%20He%20put%20the%20facts%20he%20had%20seen%20and%20gathered%20himself%20before%20his%20countrymen%20and%20women%20without%20sarcasm%20or%20cynicism.%20Despite%20his%20semantic%20limitations%2C%20the%20man%20managed%20to%20convey%20the%20pain%20of%20all%20communities%20in%20the%20beleaguered%20area%2C%20especially%20the%20women%20who%20are%20forced%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fwomans-rights-body-flags-grim-condition-at-relief-camps-in-manipur%2Farticle67037588.ece%5C%22%3E%20live%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fground-report-manipur-relief-camp%5C%22%3Erefugee%20camps%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20own%20state.%20Even%20to%20the%20most%20cynical%20members%20of%20the%20audience%2C%20the%20incidents%20he%20recounted%20and%20the%20conclusions%20he%20drew%20seemed%20far%20more%20gut-wrenching%20than%20the%20precise%20data%20put%20out%20later%20at%20length%20by%20the%20home%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20%E2%80%93%20a%20constantly%20evolving%20dream%20of%20unification%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20had%20a%20strange%20reflective%20quality.%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20India%3F%E2%80%99%20he%20asked%20rhetorically.%20How%20truly%20inclusive%20is%20the%20India%20of%20our%20dreams%20today%20where%20the%20Kukis%20and%20the%20Meiteis%2C%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Muslims%2C%20the%20state%20police%20and%20the%20Army%20stand%20snarling%20at%20each%20other%3F%20These%20tendencies%20are%20not%20just%20limited%20to%20Manipur%20but%20have%20alarmingly%20crept%20up%20and%20revealed%20themselves%20in%20far%20away%20Nuh%20and%20also%20the%20trifurcated%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20anguished%20words%20alleging%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20instead%20of%20putting%20out%20fires%20was%20spraying%20inflammable%20material%20and%20throwing%20in%20a%20match%20to%20ignite%20communal%20fires%2C%20drew%20an%20uproar%20of%20protest%20from%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20saffron%20party.%20Gandhi%20continued%20unphased.%20His%20references%20to%20his%20own%20mother%20and%20Bharat%20Mata%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-diary-parts-of-rahul-gandhis-speech-expunged-and-missing-sansad-tv-camera-angles%5C%22%3Esince%20expunged%20from%20records%3C%2Fa%3E)%20reminded%20one%20of%20Obama%E2%80%99s%20poignant%20reference%20in%20his%20autobiography%20to%20someone%20raised%20by%20a%20single%20parent%20%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20as%20that%20spell%20was%20broken%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%A6%20they%20had%20left%20behind%2C%20reclaimed%20each%E2%80%A6I%20occupied%20the%20space%20where%20their%20dreams%20had%20been%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20referring%20to%20his%20birth%20mother%20or%20Bharat%20Mata%2C%20Gandhi%20spoke%20not%20of%20his%20personal%20inheritance%20but%20of%20a%20collective%20dream%20space%20the%20generation%20of%20%3Cem%3EMidnight%E2%80%99s%20Children%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20begin%20to%20shape%20and%20reshape%20for%20their%20children.%20India%20of%20the%201980s%20was%20changing%20fast%20with%20travel%20and%20the%20Internet%20and%20inter-community%20relationships%20becoming%20commonplace%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20your%20own%20personal%20ethnic%20multiplicity%20is%20evident%2C%20as%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20many%20other%20Indians%20of%20his%20generation%20and%20the%20generations%20that%20follow%2C%20India%20emerges%20as%20a%20constantly%20evolving%20dream%20of%20unification%20%E2%80%93%20creating%20a%20peaceful%20and%20just%20democratic%20space%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20occupy%20the%20space%20they%20are%20demanding%20is%20to%20be%20really%20free%20to%20re-enter%20a%20collective%20dream.%20The%20fast-disappearing%20dream%20of%20which%20Nehru%20spoke%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Ravi%20as%20he%20unfurled%20the%20tricolor%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947.%20Seventy-five%20years%20later%2C%20the%20world%20our%20young%20occupy%20gives%20them%20or%20us%20with%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20mix%20languages%2C%20communicate%20and%20travel%20globally%2C%20riding%20the%20social%20media%20flowing%20around%20us%20in%20many%20languages.%20But%20hello%2C%20your%20mother%20remains%20your%20mother%20and%20so%20also%20your%20mother%20tongue!%20Why%20use%20sophistry%20to%20stigmatise%20the%20mixed%20lineage%20and%20cultural%20adaptability%20patriotism%20of%20the%20young%2C%20sneeringly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20demanding%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20national%20language%2C%20one%20civil%20code%20%E2%80%93%20who%20rage%20in%20the%20social%20media%2C%20in%20newspaper%20columns%2C%20in%20election%20speeches%20against%20racial%20mixing%2C%20against%20love%20marriages%2C%20against%20women%20not%20keeping%20to%20their%20assigned%20space%20in%20a%20male-dominated%20world%20%E2%80%93%20are%20liars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20have%20sent%20their%20own%20progeny%20abroad%20for%20higher%20studies%20even%20as%20they%20demand%20vernacular-based%20education%20for%20all%20Indians.%20They%20post%20photos%20of%20their%20children%20on%20graduation%20day%20with%20the%20mortar%20board%20hats%20but%20back%20home%20demand%20women%20dress%20in%20proper%20clothes%2C%20not%20torn%20jeans%20or%20skirts.%20They%20have%20long%20been%20waiting%2C%20obsessively%2C%20to%20see%20Sonia%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20mask%20of%20a%20traditional%20Indian%20woman%20slip.%20It%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20happened%20but%20they%20worry%20when%20they%20hear%20Gandhi%20speaking%20this%20way%20about%20his%20mother%20and%20Bharat%20Mata%20in%20the%20same%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20post-globalised%20world%2C%20seeking%20new%20international%20alliances%20and%20creating%20new%20workflow%20systems%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20hybridisation%20and%20connectivity%20needs%20are%20undeniable.%20Given%20how%20often%20any%20prime%20minister%20must%20travel%20abroad%20with%20his%20ministers%20to%20showcase%20his%20nation%20as%20an%20attractive%20investment%20destination%2C%20can%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20interactions%20be%20made%20to%20look%20threatening%20in%202024%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20fear%20is%20that%20Gandhi%20has%20taken%20to%20marching%20through%20the%20country%20and%20could%20become%20a%20witness-turned-participant%20in%20a%20sudden%20upheaval.%20By%20next%20year%2C%20his%20anger%20may%20begin%20resonating%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20officially%20young.%20If%20a%20man%20in%20his%20early%2050s%2C%20born%20of%20a%20mixed%20parentage%20with%20no%20family%20baggage%20of%20his%20own%2C%20begins%20to%20attract%20attention%20all%20through%20this%20diverse%20country%20by%20walking%20around%2C%20who%20knows%20he%20may%20go%20on%20to%20reveal%20some%20terrible%20unseen%20landmines%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20as%20a%20democracy%20is%20finally%20approaching%20a%20point%20in%20history%20where%20our%20basic%20identity%20remains%20rooted%20in%20the%20dream%20space%20created%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Ambedkar%2C%20Gandhi%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Patel%2C%20and%20Maulana%20Azad.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20think%20if%20we%20appreciate%20hybridised%20languages%2C%20voices%20and%20multiple%20sensibilities%20in%20our%20artists%2C%20why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20we%20appreciate%20these%20very%20qualities%20in%20our%20politicians%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691906406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F12150823%2FIMG_6738.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgiving-india-a-voice-amid-the-shifting-political-landscape%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20truly%20inclusive%20is%20the%20India%20of%20our%20dreams%20today%20where%20the%20Kukis%20and%20the%20Meiteis%2C%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Muslims%2C%20the%20state%20police%20and%20the%20Army%20stand%20snarling%20at%20each%20other%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgiving-india-a-voice-amid-the-shifting-political-landscape%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electricity%20output%20sees