0the%20spirit%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPradhan%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20%E2%80%9Chave%20always%20been%20vociferous%20about%20promoting%20and%20preserving%20India%E2%80%99s%20linguistic%20diversity%2C%20including%20Tamil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKashi%20Tamil%20Sangamam%20was%20one%20such%20glowing%20example.%20And%2C%20this%20causes%20heartache%20to%20those%20who%20have%20a%20misplaced%20thought%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20continuum%20and%20literary%20pride%20is%20propriety%20of%20a%20few%20dynasts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShashiTharoor%2Fstatus%2F1690300916145270784%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20reaction%20%E2%80%9Cis%20hardly%20surprising%20%26amp%3B%20should%20have%20been%20anticipated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20have%20cost%20the%20government%20little%20to%20have%20the%20names%20of%20the%20new%20Bills%20in%20both%20Hindi%20and%20English%20(as%20required%20by%20Article%20348%20of%20the%20constitution)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20chose%20to%20rub%20their%20Hindi%20chauvinism%20into%20the%20faces%20of%20everyone%20else%20%26amp%3B%20have%20thus%20undone%20all%20the%20efforts%20made%20by%20the%20PM%20%26amp%3B%20other%20ministers%20to%20praise%20Tamil%E2%80%99s%20rich%20legacy%20%26amp%3B%20hail%20Tamil%20culture%20at%20every%20opportunity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYet%20another%20own-goal%20by%20the%20petty%20minds%20in%20the%20BJP!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20348%20(b)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F928281%2F%5C%22%3Estates%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20all%20Bills%20or%20amendments%20to%20be%20moved%20in%20either%20House%20of%20parliament%20or%20state%20legislature%2C%20all%20acts%20passed%20by%20parliament%20or%20state%20legislatures%2C%20ordinances%20passed%20by%20the%20President%20or%20state%20governors%2C%20and%20all%20orders%2C%20rules%2C%20regulations%20and%20bye%20laws%20issued%20under%20the%20Constitution%20or%20under%20any%20law%20made%20by%20Parliament%20or%20the%20Legislature%20of%20a%20State%2C%20shall%20be%20in%20the%20English%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20also%20adds%20that%20in%20the%20instance%20of%20laws%20being%20made%20by%20state%20legislatures%20in%20any%20other%20Indian%20language%2C%20a%20translation%20needs%20to%20be%20available%20of%20the%20text%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20DMK%20MP%20P.%20Wilson%20had%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20move%20to%20name%20the%20new%20Bills%20in%20Hindi%20is%20%E2%80%9Cyet%20another%20form%20of%20Hindi%20imposition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShocked%20to%20see%20names%20of%20new%20IPC%2C%20CrPC%20and%20Evidence%20Act%20in%20Hindi.%20Maybe%20the%20Hon.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20has%20not%20seen%20Article%20348%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%3F%20Names%20of%20Bills%20%26amp%3B%20Acts%20must%20be%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20yet%20another%20form%20of%20Hindi%20imposition.%20South%20Indian%20lawyers%20are%20going%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTuXAjqpcdL%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTuXAjqpcdL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20P.%20Wilson%20(%40PWilsonDMK)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPWilsonDMK%2Fstatus%2F1689976175572217856%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSouth%20Indian%20lawyers%20are%20going%20to%20spend%20most%20of%20the%20time%20in%20courts%20trying%20to%20pronounce%20these%20names.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Mohan%20Katarki%20has%20also%20criticised%20the%20naming%20of%20the%20new%20Bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHindi%20title%20in%20English%20version%20of%20the%20Bill%20is%20wholly%20arbitrary%20and%20unconstitutional.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20attempt%20to%20impose%20Hindi%20on%20non-Hindi%20people.%20Even%20otherwise%2C%20changes%20are%20superficial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmohankatarki%2Fstatus%2F1689977632342085633%5C%22%3Esaid.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eearlier%2C%20senior%20advocate%20in%20Delhi%20high%20court%20Sanjoy%20Ghose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsedition-law-repealed-three-new-bills-tabled-in-parliament-to-replace-criminal-laws%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunheard%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20legislations%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Ordinances%20or%20Bills%20have%20a%20Hindi%20and%20an%20English%20version.%20But%20this%20is%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20they%20have%20given%20the%20English%20version%20a%20Hindi%20name%20and%20forced%20a%20Hindi%20name%20on%20English%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20this%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20light%20of%20a%20very%20Brahmincal%20Hindi%20imposition%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20I%20say%20this%20is%20that%20is%20a%20very%20Sanskritised%20Hindi%20name%20that%20they%20have%20given%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20it%20could%20have%20been%20named%20simply%20Bharatiya%20Danda%20Kosh%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20but%20instead%20it%20is%20called%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%20Sanskritised%20Hindi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691902803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25203412%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-8.33.25-PM.png%22%2C%22