2C%20borne%20out%20of%20the%20rage%20and%20fury%20of%20the%20community%2C%20directed%20towards%20the%20state%20government%20being%20seen%20to%20be%20led%20by%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20acting%20as%20a%20polarising%20figure%20for%20his%20own%20people%2C%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U-300x147.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U-1024x501.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664089%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22587%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40NBirenSingh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20growing%20demand%20will%20not%20only%20put%20the%20Kukis%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20Meitei%20community%20but%20also%20the%20Nagas%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20rake%20up%20old%20festering%20disagreements%20between%20these%20communities%20around%20their%20different%20ideas%20about%20%E2%80%98traditional%20land%E2%80%99%20in%20that%20northeastern%20state.%20If%20what%20is%20unfolding%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Manipur%20is%20any%20indication%2C%20the%20ball%20has%20already%20started%20rolling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProposed%20Kuki%20state%20map%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20reliable%20sources%2C%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20spearheading%20the%20demand%2C%20is%20set%20to%20hand%20over%20a%20proposed%20map%20of%20sorts%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20around%20August%2017.%20Such%20a%20move%20is%20not%20just%20novel%20but%20bold%20too%2C%20since%20the%20Kuki%20community%20leaders%20know%20well%20that%20Meties%20and%20Nagas%20would%20both%20contest%20it%20tooth%20and%20nail%20%E2%80%93%20ultimately%20complicating%20their%20goal%20for%20statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fspecial-days-before-mha-was-to-finalise-kuki-accord-not-supported-by-cm-violence-broke-out-in-manipur%5C%22%3ESpecial%3A%20Manipur%20Violence%20Broke%20Out%20Days%20Before%20MHA%20Was%20to%20Finalise%20Kuki%20Accord%20that%20CM%20Did%20Not%20Support%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20sources%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%2C%20the%20talks%20around%20the%20possibility%20of%20granting%20the%20Kuki%20community%20a%20territorial%20council%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20were%20around%20Churachandpur%2C%20the%20Kuki-majority%20district%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20some%20Kuki-dominated%20strips%20of%20the%20Kangpokpi%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20the%20Centre%20had%20granted%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20to%20a%20hill%20district%20of%20Manipur%20as%20reported%20in%20the%20first%20part%20of%20this%20series%2C%20it%20would%20have%20likely%20kicked%20up%20massive%20discontent%20within%20the%20Meities%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%2C%20fanning%20an%20already%20existing%20%E2%80%98fear%E2%80%99%20within%20the%20majority%20community.%20The%20%E2%80%98fear%E2%80%99%20usually%20spoken%20of%20is%20that%2090%25%20of%20the%20land%20would%20go%20out%20of%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Meitei%20(majority)%20community%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20in%20the%20remaining%2010%25%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20restrictions%20on%20anyone%20else%20to%20settle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20fuelling%20the%20fight%20to%20maintain%20the%20%E2%80%98territorial%20integrity%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20state.%20Manipur%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20such%20sentiment%2C%20and%20in%20the%20past%2C%20this%20has%20led%20to%20events%20like%20the%20burning%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20(when%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20had%20been%20pressured%20to%20include%20the%20issue%20of%20Nagalim%20with%20the%20NSCN%20%E2%80%93I-M%20leaders%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20peace%20talks).%20So%20this%20should%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20that%2C%20with%20the%20Kuki%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20state%2C%20the%20agitation%20to%20maintain%20the%20%E2%80%98territorial%20integrity%E2%80%99%20of%20Manipur%20has%20yet%20again%20gained%20steam%2C%20led%20by%20powerful%20civil%20society%20organisations%20like%20the%20Meira%20Paibi%20and%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%C2%A0Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F28224742%2Fmeira-paibis.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22760%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F28224742%2Fmeira-paibis.jpeg%20760w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F28224742%2Fmeira-paibis-300x175.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-621820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20Meira%20Paibis.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Meiteis%20have%20been%20contesting%20some%20lands%20claimed%20by%20the%20Kukis%20as%20their%20own.%20That%20Churachandpur%20has%20two%20names%20%E2%80%93%20called%20Lamka%20by%20the%20Kukis%20and%20Churachandpur%20by%20the%20Meities%2C%20drawing%20from%20the%20name%20of%20a%20king%20from%20the%20community%20%E2%80%93%20is%20only%20one%20such%20example%20of%20contestation%20about%20who%20has%20claim%20over%20the%20land%20historically.%20This%20is%20a%20highly%20sensitive%20issue%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20kept%20in%20check%20with%20the%20best%20version%20of%20the%20politics%20of%20accommodation.%20Inept%20handling%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20can%20easily%20tip%20the%20balance%20and%20unspool%20into%20acrimony%20%E2%80%93%20as%20their%20respective%20%E2%80%98histories%E2%80%99%20are%20then%20easily%20revived%20and%20end%20up%20rekindling%20old%20antagonisms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdd%20to%20this%2C%20the%20overlapping%20of%20claims%20over%20land%20by%20the%20Nagas%20and%20the%20Kukis%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20makes%20it%20a%20tinderbox.%20Including%20Churachandpur%20in%20a%20proposed%20Kuki%20state%20map%20will%20mean%20zero%20trouble%20with%20the%20Nagas%2C%20but%20including%20the%20entire%20Kangpokpi%20district%20would%20spell%20trouble.%20According%20to%20reliable%20sources%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20the%20ITLF%E2%80%99s%20proposed%20map%20for%20a%20Kuki%20state%20does%20include%20the%20Kangpokpi%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20was%20carved%20out%20of%20Naga-dominated%20Senapati%20district%20in%202016%20by%20the%20then%20Congress%20government.%20It%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20strategic%20game%20plan%20of%20the%20then-Okram%20Ibobi%20Singh%20government%20to%20strike%20at%20the%20Nagas%2C%20purportedly%20as%20outreach%20to%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%20who%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20Naga%20demand%20for%20greater%20Nagalim%20or%20unification%20of%20Naga-dominated%20areas%20across%20north-eastern%20states.%20The%20reasoning%20was%20that%20this%20would%20keep%20the%20flock%20away%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20which%20was%20threatening%20to%20topple%20his%20government%20in%20the%20coming%20polls.%20Meitei%20votes%20are%20crucial%20for%20a%20party%20to%20win%20the%20state%20elections%20as%2040%20of%20the%2060%20seats%20are%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%20which%20are%20Meitei-dominated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20Kangpokpi%2C%20but%20the%20creation%20of%20newer%20districts%20then%2C%20like%20Noney%20from%20the%20Naga-dominated%20Tamenglong%20district%2C%20Kamjong%20from%20Naga-dominated%20Ukhrul%2C%20and%20Tengnoupal%20from%20Naga-dominated%20Chandel%20district%20got%20the%20Ibobi%20Singh%20government%20into%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20the%20United%20Naga%20Council%20(UNC)%2C%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20the%20Nagas%20in%20Manipur.%20UNC%20saw%20the%20move%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98Meitei%20CM%E2%80%99%20to%20take%20away%20the%20%E2%80%98traditional%20land%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Nagas.%20Protests%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKangpokpi%20also%20has%20a%20Meitei%20presence%2C%20even%20if%20small%2C%20and%20this%20would%20mean%20that%20not%20just%20the%20Nagas%20but%20the%20Meiteis%20would%20also%20have%20a%20stake%20in%20fighting%20to%20keep%20the%20district%20out%20of%20the%20proposed%20map%20for%20a%20Kuki%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20roadblock%20is%20that%20Kangpokpi%20shares%20borders%20with%20the%20valley%20(Imphal%20East%20and%20West%20districts)%20aside%20from%20Naga-dominated%20Senapati%20and%20Tamenglong%20districts%20and%20has%20no%20contiguity%20with%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20Churachandpur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20as%20is%20reliably%20learnt%2C%20the%20ITLF%E2%80%99s%20proposed%20map%20also%20includes%20some%20strips%20of%20the%20Naga-dominated%20Chandel%20district%20which%20shares%20borders%20with%20Churachandpur.%20Already%2C%20the%20Nagas%20are%20upset%20with%20slicing%20out%20the%20Tengnoupal%20district%20from%20it%20in%202016.%20No%20wonder%20then%20that%20Assam%20Rifles%20saying%20on%20July%2023%20that%20718%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%20(of%20Chin-Zo%20origin)%20had%20entered%20Chandel%20just%20in%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20time%20prodded%20the%20UNC%20to%20call%20for%20an%20update%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20in%20the%20state.%20UNC%E2%80%99s%20reaction%20must%20also%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20context%20of%20them%20being%20projected%20as%20officially%20the%20largest%20contingent%20of%20%E2%80%98illegal%20migrants%E2%80%99%20from%20strife-torn%20Myanmar%20streaming%20into%20Manipur.%20In%20the%20demand%20for%20an%20NRC%2C%20both%20UNC%20of%20the%20Nagas%20and%20the%20Meitei%20CSO%20COCOMI%20are%20on%20the%20same%20page%20while%20the%20Kuki%20CSOs%20like%20ITLF%20are%20vehemently%20opposed%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20background%20of%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20Kuki%20state%20being%20raised%20by%20the%20community%20with%20Delhi%2C%20the%20divisions%20with%20the%20Nagas%20are%20only%20getting%20sharper.%20On%20August%209%2C%20UNC%20held%20rallies%20across%20the%20Naga-dominated%20districts%20of%20Chandel%2C%20Ukhrul%2C%20Tamenglong%20and%20Senapati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Func-all-set-for-rally%5C%22%3EA%20memorandum%20submitted%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20rally%20not%20only%20demanded%20that%20the%20Naga%20issue%20be%20expedited%20based%20on%20the%20Framework%20Agreement%20signed%20with%20the%20NSCN%20(I-M)%20in%202015%20but%20also%20explicitly%20stated%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98Naga%20areas%E2%80%99%20must%20not%20be%20touched%20by%20the%20Centre.%20Media%20reports%20said%20UNC%20general%20secretary%20Ayo%20Satsang%20warned%20the%20Centre%20against%20going%20ahead%20with%20any%20settlement%20of%20the%20demands%20by%20other%20communities%20(hinting%20at%20the%20Kukis)%20that%20may%20affect%20the%20Naga%20areas%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20said%20to%20be%20looking%20at%20settling%20some%20Kuki%20families%20displaced%20by%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20an%20area%20of%20the%20Kangpokpi%20district%20which%20is%20considered%20by%20the%20Liangmai%20Nagas%20as%20their%20traditional%20land.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Frally-manipur-resolution-naga-political-issue-8885882%2F%5C%22%3EOn%20August%2010%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20delegation%20of%20Liangmai%20Nagas%20met%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20pointedly%20oppose%20such%20a%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevelopments%20like%20the%20UNC%20rally%20and%20the%20Liangmai%20Nagas%E2%80%99%20appeal%20to%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20are%20increasingly%20leading%20to%20Kuki%20leaders%20stating%20in%20the%20media%20that%20their%20statehood%20demand%20is%20not%20getting%20enough%20support%20from%20the%20Nagas.%20Till%20now%2C%20though%20the%20Nagas%20of%20Manipur%20have%20been%20taking%20a%20neutral%20position%20in%20the%20clash%20between%20the%20Meites%20and%20the%20Kukis%2C%20it%20has%20also%20provided%20the%20much-needed%20help%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%20in%20New%20Delhi%20to%20file%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20its%20intervention%20to%20quell%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Manipur-based%20Naga%20leader%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20fully%20support%20if%20the%20Kukis%20are%20granted%20Sixth%20Schedule%20by%20the%20Centre%20centering%20around%20Churachandpur%20but%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20agree%20if%20it%20lays%20claim%20to%20our%20traditional%20land%2C%20that%20too%20at%20a%20time%20when%20our%20political%20movement%20is%20at%20a%20crucial%20phase.%E2%80%9D%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20as%20hill%20people%20of%20Manipur%2C%20have%20many%20issues%20in%20common%2C%20such%20as%20forest%20rights%2C%20need%20for%20development%20of%20our%20areas%2C%20etc.%2C%20but%20the%20land%20is%20a%20sensitive%20issue%20where%20there%20is%20no%20compromise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKuki%20homeland%3A%20Longstanding%20demand%20and%20roadblocks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20decades%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20Kuki%20homeland%20has%20met%20a%20roadblock%20only%20because%20of%20contestations%20over%20traditional%20land.%20The%20notion%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98separate%20administration%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20Kukis%20has%2C%20over%20time%2C%20taken%20various%20forms%20including%20demanding%20unification%20of%20all%20Kuki-Zo%20areas%20(this%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Mizoram%20political%20movement%20of%20the%201960s)%3B%20to%20Kukiland%E2%80%99%20(this%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20formation%20of%20Kuki%20armed%20groups%20like%20the%20United%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20and%20Kuki%20National%20Army%20in%20the%201980s)%3B%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98state%20within%20a%20state%E2%80%99%20under%20Article%20244A%2C%20(much%20like%20what%20Meghalaya%20was%20granted%20by%20New%20Delhi%20before%20it%20became%20a%20full-fledged%20state)%3B%20to%20seeking%20autonomous%20territorial%20council%20within%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-ahead-of-polls-mnfs-renewed-call-for-zo-unification-creates-political-flutter%5C%22%3EMizoram%3A%20Ahead%20of%20Polls%2C%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20Renewed%20Call%20for%20Zo%20Unification%20Creates%20Political%20Flutter%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20while%20holding%20talks%20with%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20first%20interlocutor%20Dineshwar%20Sharma%2C%20the%20Kuki%20SoO%20groups%20were%20seeking%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstate%20within%20a%20state%E2%80%9D%20under%20Article%20244A.%20Their%20leaders%20had%20seen%20such%20a%20demand%20to%20the%20Centre%20as%20a%20tactical%20move%20and%20a%20precursor%20to%20a%20Kuki%20state%20in%20the%20course%20of%20time.%20However%2C%20on%20MHA%E2%80%99s%20prodding%2C%20over%20time%2C%20the%20demand%20was%20diluted%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98Bodo-like%20territorial%20council%E2%80%99%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20which%2C%20as%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20in%20the%20first%20part%20of%20this%20series%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnortheast-manipur-mizoram-majauli%5C%22%3Ewas%20nearly%20granted%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20change%20of%20vocabulary%20from%20%E2%80%98separate%20administration%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98complete%20separation%E2%80%99%20post-May%203%20violence%20is%20being%20interpreted%20by%20various%20Kuki-Zo%20leaders%20from%20Manipur%20and%20Mizoram%20as%20statehood%2C%20Union%20territory%20status%20or%20joining%20Mizoram%2C%20a%20land%20contiguous%20with%20Churachandpur%2C%20the%20Kuki%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1-300x162.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1-1024x554.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662929%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22649%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20EastMojo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20while%20the%20political%20talks%20till%20now%20were%20being%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20(SoO)%20groups%20(under%20ceasefire)%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20ITLF%20is%20a%20new%20player%2C%20though%20its%20leaders%20have%20lately%20been%20saying%20that%20the%20peace%20talks%20would%20be%20taken%20forward%20with%20the%20Centre%20only%20by%20the%20SoO%20groups.%20But%2C%20MHA%20sources%20say%20Delhi%20can%E2%80%99t%20fully%20ignore%20the%20ITLF%20as%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20presenting%20itself%20as%20representing%20Kuki%20public%20sentiments%2C%20a%20reason%20why%20SoO%20groups%20are%20also%20no%20more%20willing%20to%20agree%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20but%20want%20to%20talk%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20statehood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMHA%20sources%20told%20this%20correspondent%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20is%20also%20a%20problem.%20The%20ITLF%20is%20only%20Churachandpur%20based%3B%20our%20feedback%20from%20the%20ground%20is%20some%20Kukis%2C%20say%20from%20Moreh%2C%20etc.%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20consider%20ITLF%20as%20representative%20of%20their%20interests.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20are%20keen%20to%20take%20forward%20the%20talks%20with%20the%20SoO%20groups%20only%2C%20but%20with%20the%20new%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20state%20from%20ITLF%20which%20has%20found%20resonance%20within%20the%20community%2C%20and%20is%20being%20vehemently%20opposed%20by%20the%20Meitei%20groups%2C%20and%20most%20likely%20by%20the%20Nagas%20too%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20quick%20solution%20to%20the%20issue.%20First%20and%20foremost%2C%20we%20have%20to%20look%20at%20bringing%20peace%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20then%20political%20talks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20while%20various%20Congress%20regimes%20had%20created%20new%20states%20in%20the%20northeast%20over%20a%20span%20of%20decades%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20the%20matter%20has%20been%20ambivalent.%20In%20its%202014%20manifesto%2C%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fbjp-includes-gorkhaland-issue-from-its-2014-election-manifesto%2Farticleshow%2F33461346.cms%5C%22%3Ehad%20included%20support%20for%20Bodoland%20and%20Gorkhaland%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reaped%20electoral%20benefits%20on%20such%20promises%2C%20it%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheshillongtimes.com%2F2014%2F07%2F02%2Fbodos-want-modi-government-to-deli