0when%20committing%20the%20killings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fjust-not-safe-kin-of-train-shooting-victim-says-of-living-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anwaarul%20Haq%20Kakar%2C%20Balochistan%20Senator%2C%20Named%20Pakistan's%20Caretaker%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F12193708%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-12T193701.021.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20a%20significant%20delay%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20President%20Arif%20Alvi%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%2012%2C%20assented%20to%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20relatively%20low-profile%20senator%20from%20Baluchistan%20Awami%20Party%20(BAP)%2C%20Anwaarul%20Haq%20Kakar%2C%20as%20the%20caretaker%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20in%20the%20appointment%20was%20due%20to%20differences%20between%20the%20military%20establishment%20and%20civilian%20government%20over%20zeroing%20in%20on%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20was%20made%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%2012%2C%20by%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly%2C%20Raja%20Riaz%2C%20while%20talking%20to%20reporters%20outside%20his%20office%20in%20Islamabad.%20Later%2C%20a%20press%20release%20from%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Shahbaz%20Sharif%20and%20Riaz%20had%20jointly%20sent%20advice%20to%20President%20Alvi%20for%20Kakar%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20as%20interim%20head%20of%20government.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPresOfPakistan%2Fstatus%2F1690314447695585280%5C%22%3EAlvi%20approved%20the%20appointment%3C%2Fa%3E%20shortly%20afterwards%2C%20with%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20to%20be%20held%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1769757%2Fbaps-anwaarul-haq-kakar-to-be-caretaker-pm%5C%22%3EAs%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Riaz%20told%20reporters%20that%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20caretaker%20PM%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20be%20someone%20from%20a%20smaller%20province%20and%20a%20non-controversial%20personality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20indicated%20that%20Kakar%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20his%20proposal.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20given%20this%20name%20and%20the%20PM%20has%20consented%20to%20this%20name%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20and%20the%20PM%20have%20signed%20on%20the%20summary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20BAP%20was%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20headed%20by%20Sharif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20newspaper%2C%20Kakar%20was%20elected%20as%20an%20independent%20senator%20from%20Balochistan%20in%20March%202018.%20Soon%20after%2C%20he%20co-founded%20the%20Balochistan%20Awami%20Party%20(BAP)%20along%20with%20another%20leader.%20BAP%20emerged%20as%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20Balochistan%20in%20the%202018%20general%20elections.%20From%20the%20start%2C%20it%20had%20been%20speculated%20that%20BAP%20was%20the%20favoured%20political%20party%20of%20the%20army%20in%20the%20province%2C%20but%20party%20leaders%20claimed%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F1774980%2Fbap-rejects-rumours-establishment-support-polls%5C%22%3Ecriticism%20smacked%20of%20jealousy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Pakistan%20media%2C%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20caretaker%20prime%20minister%20after%20the%20national%20assembly%20was%20dissolved%20on%20August%209%20was%20due%20to%20differences%20between%20the%20Nawaz%20Sharif-led%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20party%20and%20the%20military%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiaz%20had%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98friendly%E2%80%99%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20but%20he%20had%20been%20surprisingly%20intransigent%2C%20even%20refusing%20to%20accept%20requests%20for%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20grounds%20of%20a%20busy%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%E2%80%99s%20first%20choice%20as%20caretaker%20prime%20minister%20had%20been%20the%20highly%20unpopular%20finance%20minister%20and%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20father-in-law%2C%20Ishaq%20Dar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20Riaz%2C%20a%20PTI%20dissident%20with%20no%20backing%20of%20a%20political%20party%2C%20was%20getting%20dictation%20from%20another%20power%20corridor%20and%20insisting%20on%20the%20name%20of%20Senate%20Chairman%20Sadiq%20Sanjrani%2C%20sources%20claimed.%20Sanjrani%20called%20on%20Riaz%20on%20Friday%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Dar%20and%20Ahsan%20Iqbal%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenews.com.pk%2Flatest%2F1099503-caretaker-pm-name-likely-to-be-finalised-today%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Geo%20news%20anchor%20Shahzeb%20Khanzada%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20from%20the%20beginning%20that%20if%20the%20politician%20was%20a%20nominee%20of%20the%20politicians%2C%20the%20name%20would%20be%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20the%20individual%20was%20a%20nominee%20of%20the%20state%2C%20the%20name%20would%20be%20presented%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition.%20As%20expected%2C%20the%20latter%20scenario%20has%20unfolded%2C%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20job%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20to%20support%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20and%20conduct%20the%20day-to-day%20affairs%20of%20governance.%20However%2C%20the%20last%20National%20Assembly%20passed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fexplainer-pakistan-has-just-given-more-powers-to-its-caretaker-government-and-it-is-not-good-news%5C%22%3Elegislation%20which%20gave%20more%20powers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20caretaker%20government%2C%20especially%20led%20to%20concern%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20delay%20in%20holding%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Shahbaz%20Sharif%20government%20approved%20holding%20the%20census%20before%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20it%20was%20confirmed%20that%20it%20was%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20the%20general%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20on%20schedule%20as%20per%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691849328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F12193708%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-12T193701.021.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fanwaarul-haq-kakar-balochistan-senator-named-pakistans-caretaker-pm%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20appointment%20came%20after%20a%20significant%20delay.%20Differences%20between%20the%20military%20establishment%20and%20civilian%20government%20over%20zeroing%20in%20on%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20job%20resulted%20in%20the%20delay.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fanwaarul-haq-kakar-balochistan-senator-named-pakistans-caretaker-pm%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Critical%20Zone%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20Film%20the%20Iranian%20Government%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Want%20to%20Be%20Seen%2C%20Wins%20in%20Locarno%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691847479000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMantagheye-bohrani-Critical-Zone_1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235694862%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20hype%20is%20real%3A%20Ali%20Ahmadzadeh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CCritical%20Zone%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%9CMantagheye%20bohrani%E2%80%9D)%20has%20picked%20up%20the%20top%20Golden%20Leopard%20at%20Locarno.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20bumpy%20ride%20for%20the%20film%2C%20set%20in%20Tehran%20over%20the%20course%