7-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-4-1691501297-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-4-1691501297-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326732%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAakriti%20helps%20pastoralists%20by%20selling%20camel%20milk-based%20products%20through%20%E2%80%98Bahula%20Naturals%E2%80%99.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%2027-year-old%20is%20able%20to%20bring%20livelihood%20opportunities%20back%20to%20these%20pastoralists%20with%20her%20startup%20%E2%80%98Bahula%20Naturals%E2%80%99.%20It%20supports%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20at%20least%202%2C500%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F146487%2Franchhod-pagi-rabari-herder-gujarat-bsf-indo-pak-war%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecamel%20herders%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20helps%20at%20least%2045%2C000%20camels%20thrive%20by%20selling%20camel%20milk-based%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCan%20you%20imagine%20deserts%20without%20camels%3F%20We%20attempt%20to%20bring%20livelihood%20opportunities%20to%20these%20communities%2C%20highly%20nutritious%20food%20for%20our%20customers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20bring%20the%20cause%20of%20camel%20conservation%20through%20these%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJournalist%20turned%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Aakriti%20moved%20to%20Bajju%20village%20in%20Bikaner%20district%20near%20the%20India-Pakistan%20border%2C%20nearly%201%2C200%20km%20from%20her%20hometown%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Gorakhpur.%20It%20was%20while%20pursuing%20her%20graduation%20in%20journalism%20and%20mass%20communication%20in%20Delhi%20that%20she%20was%20assigned%20to%20document%20stories%20of%20pastoralists%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325795%2Fretired-army-officer-colonel-mahendra-mohan-oasis-luxury-camps-in-jaisalmer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThar%20desert%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20the%20desert%20in%20June.%20All%20my%20romantic%20notions%20of%20what%20a%20desert%20would%20be%20like%20were%20shattered%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20first%20visit%20which%20was%20for%20four%20months%2C%20she%20learnt%20about%20the%20community%20of%20pastoralists%2C%20camel%20herders%2C%20sheep%20goat%20rearers%2C%20and%20indigenous%20cow%20rearers.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20challenging%20geographies%20and%20extreme%20temperatures%2C%20these%20communities%20would%20travel%20eight%20months%20on%20foot%20covering%20800%20km%20of%20stretch%20with%20their%20herds%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPastoralism%20has%20been%20enriching%20the%20desert%20soil%20all%20these%20years.%20Whatever%20organic%20greenery%20that%20we%20see%20in%20deserts%20is%20because%20of%20their%20movement.%20When%20the%20pastoralists%20are%20on%20the%20move%20with%20livestock%2C%20their%20droppings%20rejuvenate%20the%20pasture%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20sells%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20camel%20milk%20ghee%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20Cheshire%20cheese%2C%20and%20cold-pressed%20oils.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-natura