5C%22(max-width%3A%201279px)%20100vw%2C%201279px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221279%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20ecosoul%20bowl%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035.jpeg%201279w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035-240x300.jpeg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035-500x625.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035-768x961.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035-1228x1536.jpeg%201228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035-150x188.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326232%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20palm%20leaf%20bowl%20by%20EcoSoul%20Home%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20and%20Rahul%20met%20during%20their%20stint%20at%20Wayfair%2C%20an%20American%20e-commerce%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20for%20EcoSoul%20was%20born%20out%20of%20our%20experiences%20at%20Wayfair.%20We%20were%20tasked%20with%20exploring%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20sustainable%20product%20category%20for%20the%20company.%20As%20we%20delved%20deeper%20into%20the%20sustainability%20space%20and%20analysed%20consumer%20behaviour%2C%20we%20noticed%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20eco-friendly%20alternatives.%20This%20realisation%20became%20our%20%3Cem%3Eaha%3C%2Fem%3E%20moment!%20We%20recognised%20that%20the%20market%20was%20ripe%20for%20disruption%20and%20that%20sustainable%20products%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20gain%20significant%20traction%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arvind%2C%20co-founder%2C%20EcoSoul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20wave%20of%20transformation%20in%20consumer%20behaviour%20towards%20sustainability%20came%20in%20the%20food%20category.%20Today%2C%20many%20are%20consuming%20organic%2C%20unprocessed%20food.%20So%2C%20we%20figured%20the%20next%20breakout%20category%20had%20to%20be%20something%20that%20touches%20the%20food.%20For%20instance%2C%20your%20tabletop%20line%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20decided%20to%20sell.%20We%20wanted%20to%20disrupt%20this%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2040-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%20quit%20their%20jobs%20in%20June%202020%2C%20right%20when%20COVID%20was%20beginning%20to%20rear%20its%20head%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20basically%20solving%20for%20the%20three%20big%20As%20%E2%80%94%20awareness%2C%20affordability%20and%20availability.%20Awareness%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20big%20problem%20as%20most%20people%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20harm%20that%20plastic%20causes.%20We%20had%20to%20keep%20our%20prices%20within%2025%20percent%20of%20single-use%20plastic%20to%20make%20it%20affordable.%20The%20major%20challenge%20was%20availability%20as%20we%20started%20during%20COVID%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20make%20their%20products%20widely%20available%2C%20they%20had%20to%20work%20on%20a%20strong%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20this%20would%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315625%2Fdelhi-meeta-sharma-gupta-shumee-sustainable-toy-brand-develop-cognitive-motor-skills-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%20game%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20massive%20supply%20chain%20can%20only%20be%20built%20out%20of%20Asia%2C%20for%20which%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20India.%20Another%20challenge%20was%20that%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20built%20sitting%20at%20home%2C%20which%20is%20where%20the%20world%20was%20in%202020.%20We%20slowly%20worked%20around%20it%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20strong%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Singh%2C%20Co-founder%20of%20EcoSoul%20Home%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115.jpeg%201066w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115-768x1153.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115-1023x1536.jpeg%201023w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115-150x225.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326238%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERahul%20Singh%2C%20co-founder%20of%20EcoSoul%20Home%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20COVID%2C%20they%20built%20a%20supply%20chain%20in%20India%2C%20China%2C%20Thailand%2C%20and%20Mexico.%20The%20founders%20share%20how%20they%20experienced%20Murphy%E2%80%99s%20Law%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Anything%20that%20can%20go%20wrong%20will%20go%20wrong%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20when%20they%20worked%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20building%20a%20supply%20chain%20amidst%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20faced%20multiple%20challenges%20from%20raw%20material%20shortages%20to%20transportation%20bottlenecks%2C%20sky-high%20container%20prices%20and%20labour%20force%20constraints.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CFinding%20big%20players%20in%20India%20in%20this%20segment%20was%20difficult.%20In%20China%2C%20a%20sugarcane%20bagasse%20factory%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%20150-200%20tonnes%20per%20day%2C%20while%20in%20India%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20two%20tonnes.%20The%20scale%20difference%20is%20huge.%20We%20had%20to%20work%20on%20scaling%20up%2C%20which%20we%20did.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20built%20a%20large%20factory%20for%20producing%20palm%20leaf%20plates%20in%20Tumakuru%2C%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20small%20cottage%20industries%20in%20the%20palm%20leaf%20segment.%20So%20we%20worked%20with%20the%20Krishikalpa%20Foundation%20to%20build%20a%20large%20factory.%20Farmers%20from%2021%20districts%20came%20together%20and%20built%20a%20factory%20which%20has%2045%20machines%20today.%20All%20the%20products%20are%20exported%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202021%2C%20they%20started%20selling%20six%20products%2C%20including%20palm%20leaf%20plates%20and%20bamboo-based%20cutlery%20online%20in%20North%20America.%20They%20replaced%20plastic%20in%20everyday%20products%2C%20such%20as%20forks%2C%20spoons%2C%20cups%2C%20straws%2C%20plates%20etc.%20They%20also%20replaced%20paper%20with%20their%20compostable%20paper%20towels%2C%20which%20are%20actually%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20agro-waste%20to%20make%20our%20products.%20We%20work%20with%20sugarcane%20bagasse%2C%20rice%20khus%2C%20wheat%20khus%2C%20and%20palm%20leaves.%20We%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20cut%20any%20trees%20to%20make%20our%20products.%20All%20our%20finished%20products%20are%20replacements%20for%20single-use%20plastics%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rahul%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20their%20products%20are%20%E2%80%9Cearthworm%20certified.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20plastic%20or%20cut%20trees%2C%20all%20our%20products%20are%20compostable.%20It%E2%80%99s%20good%20for%20soil%20health.%20Even%20earthworms%20can%20eat%20it%20after%20it%20gets%20composted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ecosoul%20cutlery%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-1536x1536.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-cutlery-1691067315-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326248%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEco-friendly%20cutlery%20by%20EcoSoul%20Home.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20aim%20to%20provide%20consumers%20with%20credible%2C%20certified%2C%20and%20economically%20viable%20alternatives%20to%20single-use%20plastic%20products.%20Our%20vision%20is%20to%20revolutionise%20the%20sustainability%20space%20by%20addressing%20the%20critical%20challenges%20of%20awareness%2C%20availability%2C%20and%20affordability.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20empowering%20consumers%20to%20make%20conscious%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316513%2Fhow-to-set-up-eco-friendly-business-worth-crores-entrepreneur-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-conscious%20choices%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20contributing%20to%20a%20cleaner%20and%20greener%20planet%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arvind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%2042%20products%20across%20six%20categories%20%E2%80%94%20kitchen%2C%20dining%2C%20tabletop%2C%20bath%2C%20baby%20and%20personal%20care.%20They%20are%20present%20in%205%2C000%20stores%20across%2011%20countries%20including%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20Germany%2C%20UAE%2C%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEcoSoul%20launched%20in%20India%20with%20tableware%20items%20like%20palm%20leaf%20plates%2C%20cutlery%2C%20bowls%2C%20cutting%20boards%2C%20compostable%20bags%2C%20etc%20in%20December%202022.%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20we%20sell%20in%20India%20is%20made%20in%20India.%20India%20is%20our%20next%20big%20bet.%20We%20are%20already%20available%20online%20and%20are%20now%20planning%20to%20launch%20in%2010%2C000%20stores%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20products%20are%20priced%20anywhere%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Rs%20200%20to%20Rs%20800.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20using%20sustainable%20products%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20It%20is%20during%20the%20search%20for%20such%20products%20that%20I%20came%20across%20EcoSoul.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20using%20their%20palm%20leaf%20plates%20and%20dinnerware%20sets.%20They%20are%20great%20for%20parties.%20I%20like%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20compostable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonia%2C%20a%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20mistakes%20on%20their%20own%20dime%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsqopbTJZfo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp